Umubare w'abanduye coronavirus (COVID-19) mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi no mu Bwongereza wiyongereye cyane kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Umubare w'abandura coronavirus (COVID-19) ugenda wiyongera mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu k'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, ibyo bikaba byemeza ko nubwo icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri mu byiciro bitandukanye mu bihugu bitandukanye, kigenda gifata indi ntera mu bihugu byose.
Ukurikije ubunararibonye bw'u Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe bigomba kongera ubushishozi ku byerekeranye n'ubwinshi bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kuvurwa, cyane cyane kuvurwa cyane.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, hagiye haboneka abantu benshi barwaye indwara y'ibicurane by'ubwoko butaramenyekana.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'u Bushinwa gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko icyateye iyi ndwara ari ubwoko bushya bwa coronavirus, ubu buzwi nka coronavirus y'uburwayi bukomeye bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero bw'ubwoko bwa 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa na SARS-CoV-2 yatangiye kwitwa ubwandu bwa coronavirus (COVID-19).
Amakuru dufite kugeza ubu, avuga ko abagera kuri 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 barwara indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero irimo cyangwa idafite icyorezo cya Pneumonia, kandi abenshi muri abo barwaye barakira.
Hafi 14% by'abandura COVID-19 bagenda barushaho gukomera, bagasabwa kujya mu bitaro, naho 6% bagakomeza gukomera, bagasabwa kwitabwaho cyane.
Imibare y'abapfa mu barwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro ni hafi 4%.
Ubu bushakashatsi bugenzura imiterere y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU) / Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EEA) no mu Bwongereza, bugereranya n'imiterere yo mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Turasuzuma kandi imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, dukurikije imibare yo mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abandura COVID-19 mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka EAC no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu Bushinwa, cyakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu, kandi muri iki gihe, icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi gikomeje kugenda kigenda nk'uko mu Bushinwa.
Tariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyugarije isi.
Mu igazeti ya Eurosurveillance yo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, Bwana Spiteri na bagenzi be batangaje ko ari bo bantu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 mu Burayi, bakaba bari bujuje ibisabwa na OMS mu kumenya niba bafite iyo ndwara.
Abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'Uburayi/Ubukungu bw'Uburayi babonetse mu Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020  bose uko ari batatu bagarutse baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu banduye COVID-19 babonetse mu bihugu byose 30 bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, mu gihe kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza kuri uyu munsi, abantu 39 768 banduye kandi 1 727 barapfa, muri abo 17 750 harimo 1 441 bapfuye, muri icyo gihe hari mu Butaliyani honyine.
Gushyiraho umubare munini w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 n'ubwandu bw'abarwayi
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) buri munsi saa munani gisohora amakuru ku mubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi, bivuye ku makuru yemewe, urugero nk'ubushikiranganji bw'ubuzima muri ibyo bihugu, inzego z'igihugu n'akarere zishinzwe ubuzima n'ishami rya OMS.
Aya makuru akoreshwa mu gusesengura uburyo COVID-19 ikwirakwira mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/umuryango w'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'uburayi n'u Bwongereza, no kuyahura n'amakuru yo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'igaragaza ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bwa COVID-19, hakozwe ibarura ry'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu minsi 14 hashingiwe ku buryo busanzwe bwa COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone kandi, twerekanye umubare w'ubwandu buri gihugu cyagize ku isaha ya saa munani zo ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, ugereranyije n'ubw'u Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Uko COVID-19 igenda ikura mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza
Imiterere y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bw'ubwandu bw'iminsi 14 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange, yari ihuriye n'imiterere yabonetse mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Ubukungu bw'Igihugu n'u Bwongereza muri rusange watangiye kwiyongera ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, maze ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 habaho kuzamuka kw'ibipimo (inyongera).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'ubwiyongere bukabije bw'abanduye muri Italiya, ariko mu bindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, habayeho ukwiyongera nk'uko kwa COVID-19 (inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva tariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza tariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nk'uko iyi mibare ibigaragaza, umubare w'abanduye mu bihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'uburayi n'u Bwongereza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani, uhwanye n'uw'abanduye mu Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu gusa mbere yaho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu bigaragaza ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka Buraya n'u Bwongereza wiyongera cyane.
Uko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyakwirakwijwe, bigaragaza ko iki cyorezo kigenda kigenda mu buryo buhuje mu bihugu byose.
Ibi kandi n'ubwo ibihugu bitandukanye bifite uburyo butandukanye bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo, n'uburyo butandukanye bw'ubuvuzi bw'igihugu, ndetse n'uburyo butandukanye bwo kumenya ko umuntu arwaye iki cyorezo, n'uburyo butandukanye bwo guhitamo abarwayi bazakorwaho ibizamini bya COVID-19, harimo no gupima abantu.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere tw'u Butaliyani twatewe n'iki cyorezo batangaje ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi bw'indembe, kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe muri utwo turere byamaze kuzuzwa.
Kugeza ubu, amakuru y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakirwa mu bitaro no mu bigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 muri EU/EEA araboneka ku kigero cya 6% gusa n'icya 1% by'abanduye (amakuru ntabwo aratangazwa).
Ariko kandi, ni ngombwa ko hakorwa gahunda yo gukusanya ayo makuru kugira ngo yongere ku makuru y'ibyagiye bikorwa muri iki gihe, arimo umubare w'abanduye n'uw'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2010-2011 bwagaragaje ko mu Burayi hari itandukaniro rinini mu mibare y'ibitanda byo mu byumba by'indembe n'ibyumba by'indembe: mu Budage, ni 29,2 ku bantu 100.000, mu Butaliyani ho ni 4,2.
Ibi bivuze ko ibindi bihugu bishobora kuba bifite umutungo munini cyangwa muke ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12.5 by'ibitanda mu byumba by'indembe n'ibyumba by'indembe ku bantu 100.000 mu 2010-2011).
Raporo ya gatandatu ivuguruwe ya ECDC ku byerekeye ibisubizo by'ibyago bya COVID-19 byerekana imiterere y'imikorere y'ibikoresho by'ubuzima by'ubushakashatsi n'ibyerekeye imibare y'abandura COVID-19 mu bihugu byose bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, aho ibyago byo kubura ibitanda mu byumba by'indembe birenga 90%.
Kubera ko muri iki gihe, abantu banduye bashyizwe mu matsinda mu turere tumwe na tumwe tw'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'amavuriro arinda abarwayi cyane bikunze kwita ku baturage bo mu gace runaka, ni byiza ko amakuru y'ubwandu n'umubare w'ibitanda mu mavuriro arinda abarwayi cyane, ahabwa hakurikijwe ibyiciro bya 2 by'ibiro by'ibanze by'ibaruramari (NUTS-2).
Ibyaranze Ubutaliyani n'imiterere iriho mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kugenda gihinduka mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza.
Niyo mpamvu ibihugu, ibitaro n'amavuriro akomeye bigomba kwitegura icyerekezo cy'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 butavamo igihe kirekire, n'umubare wiyongera w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, cyane cyane ubuvuzi bukomeye, nk'uko bigaragara mu turere tw'u Butaliyani twatewe n'iki cyorezo.
Nk'uko raporo ya ECDC iheruka kugaragaza ibyavuye mu isesengura ry'ibyago, uburyo bwihuse, bwihuse kandi bufatika bwo guhagarika ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2 bufite akamaro kanini, nyuma yo kuva mu kugabanya ingaruka, kuko, bitewe n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'indwara, abategura ibyemezo n'ibitaro bishobora kutagira umwanya uhagije wo gutekereza, gufata no guhindura uko babyifatamo mu gihe ibyo bikorwa bitagenze neza.
Raporo y'ibyavuye mu isesengura ry'ibyago kandi irerekana ingamba zo mu rwego rw'ubuzima rusange zigamije kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Ibihugu bifite igihe gito cyo kongera imbaraga mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya ibyago byo gukwirakwira mu buvuzi.
Iyo ibyo bidakozwe, mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere, inzego z'ubuzima mu bindi bihugu byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/umuryango w'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'uburayi/ububanyi bw'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'uburayi, zishobora guhura n'ubwiyongere bw'abarwayi bakeneye ubuvuzi bukomeye.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na coronavirus y'uburwayi bukomeye bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (SARS) y'ubwoko bwa 2 (SARS-CoV-2), cyabaye ibyago ku bantu: kugeza ubu mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu by'isi hapfuye abantu barenga 3 000, umubare w'abanduye ukaba warenze 80 000.
Kimwe na virusi ya SARS-CoV ihuriyeho yatumye abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi bagerwaho n'indwara ikomeye yo guhumeka mu mwaka wa 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no kuba ituruka ku ducurama kandi igatera ibimenyetso nk'ibyo ikoresheje uburyo nk'ubwo.
Ariko COVID-19 ifite ubukana buciriritse kandi ifite igipimo cyo hasi cy'urupfu ugereranyije na SARS, ariko ni indwara yandura cyane kandi yibasira abantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko, kandi igakira abagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza umubare wiyongereye w'ibitabo bivuga kuri iyi ndwara nshya, iyi ngingo itanga isesengura ryimbitse ry'icyo kibazo cy'ubushakashatsi kirimo kigenda gihinduka mu buryo bwihuse.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ibanze biranga indwara z'ibyorezo, izifata, izifata abantu, izirebana n'ubwandu, uburyo bwo kuzisuzuma, kuzirwanya no kuzirwanya.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bitarabonerwa ibisubizo, twizeye ko ubu bushakashatsi buzatuma dusobanukirwa indwara iteje akaga kandi tukayirwanya.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi (umwaka mushya w'Ubushinwa) wabaye ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020, wabaye umunsi utazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose, kubera ko kubera icyorezo gishya cy'ubwandu bwa virusi, basabwe kuguma mu rugo mu gihe cyose cy'uwo munsi mukuru ndetse no mu byumweru byinshi nyuma yawo.
Kubera ko virusi ya corona (CoV) ari yo yatumye habaho icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze (SARS) mu 2003, ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS) wahise ushyiraho izina rya SARS-CoV-2, naho indwara ifitanye isano na yo uyita  ubwandu bwa corona 19 (COVID-19).
Icyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, cyihuta cyane kigakwira mu gihugu cyose, nyuma kigakwira mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo ku isi.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku itariki ya 2 Werurwe 2020, abasaga 80.000 bamaze kwandura COVID-19, abasaga 40.000 barakize, abasaga 3000 barapfuye.
OMS iratangaza ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi w'imbere" ku baturage kandi ko ishobora kuba iteje akaga kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, hamaze kuboneka inyandiko zirenga 200 zivuga kuri COVID-19, harimo ingingo zivuga ku byerekeye virusi, indwara z'ibyorezo, izifata, gusuzuma indwara n'uburyo bwo kuzirwanya, kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku wa 7 Mutarama 2020 yagaragaje urutonde rwa virusi yavanywe mu barwayi batandukanye.
Iyi raporo igerageza gusobanura muri rusange ibyagezweho mu bushakashatsi mu gice gishya kandi gikura vuba.
Aho bishoboka tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na coronavirus  coronavirus y'uburwayi bwo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS), yateye mu 2012.
Tuzasuzuma kandi ibintu bizwi muri iki gihe ku birebana no kwirinda indwara no kuzirinda, hamwe n'ibindi bibazo by'ingenzi.
Koronavirusi zisanzwe ari zimwe mu ndwara zitera indwara zidakomeretsa abantu kandi ahanini zitera 15% by'indwara zose zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero 4.
Nyamara, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye n'indwara z'ubwandu bwa coronavirus z'abantu inshuro ebyiri, ari zo SARS-CoV-2 na MERS-CoV, zatangiriye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, nyuma zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi, zifite ubukana buteye ubwoba bw'indwara n'urupfu.
Ku bw'ibyo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya coronavirus mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa ku ishusho ya 1.1, raporo y'ubwandu bw'ibicurane by'uburwayi bw'ibicurane butaramenyekana bwa mbere yageze muri Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima ya Chine i Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Hashize iminsi irindwi, basohoye umurongo wa virusi.
Ku itariki ya 15 Mutarama 2020, ni bwo umuntu wa mbere wapfuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu mijyi, intara n'ibihugu by'ibituranyi.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, byamenyekanye ko abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi banduye, ibyo bikaba byaratumye abantu batekereza ko virusi ishobora kwandura umuntu ku wundi.
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, mu mujyi wa Wuhan hashyizweho gahunda yo kwirinda abantu, imodoka z'abaturage zo mu mujyi zirakurwaho.
