SARS-CoV-2 ifite aho ihuriye na SARS-CoV kurusha MERS-CoV.
Hakoreshejwe microscopie ifungura mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga, ibice bya SARS-CoV-2 byabonetse mu bice by'ibinyamushongo by'ubuhumekero bw'umuntu.
Byagaragaye ko enzymes ACE2 y'umuntu ari yo ikora ku SARS-CoV-2, kimwe na SARS-CoV.
Ariko, poroteyine ya S ya SARS-CoV-2 ifata ingirabuzimafatizo ya ACE2 y'umuntu mu buryo buciriritse kurusha SARS-CoV, ibyo bikaba bisobanura ko SARS-CoV-2 ituma abarwayi barwara indwara zidakomeye cyane kurusha SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kandi gukora poroteyine y'ubuzima bugufi itari izwi mbere, yitwa orf3b, na poroteyine ihoraho, yitwa orf8.
Poroteyine ya orf3b ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira uruhare runaka mu buryo bwa virusi butera indwara no guhagarika imikorere ya IFNβ; ariko orf8 nta mwanya cyangwa imiterere izwi ifite.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ry'abanditsi bayobowe na Zhou batanze raporo ku byerekeranye na cryoelectronic tomography y'imiterere y'umushongi w'umuntu ACE2 ufite ubunini 2,9 Å hamwe na transportateur ya amino acide B0AT1.
Basanze iyi kompanyi, yari igizwe n'ibisobanuro by'ibanga ry'ibanga ry'ibanga ry'ibanga ry'ibanga, ari yo ACE2-B0AT1, ishobora guhuza poroteyine ebyiri za S, ibyo bikaba ari igihamya cy'uko virusi ya corona ishobora kumenyekana kandi ikabasama.
B0AT1 ishobora kuba igitero cyo kuvura mu gihe cyo gukora ibizamini by'imiti yo guhashya SARS-CoV-2.
Aho byaturutse n'uwari ubitunze
Birazwi ko SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV byaturutse ku ducurama, aho virusi yanduriraga ku bantu binyuze mu nyamaswa z'inkazi n'ingamiya.
Mu kugereranya SARS-CoV-2 n'izindi virusi bya koronavirusi, byemejwe ko SARS-CoV-2 ya mbere yafashwe n'imbeba kuko virusi nshya ifite 96% y'ubwoko bwa virusi ebyiri za SARS, ari zo SL-CoVZX45 na SL-CoVZX21.
Icyakora, ntibiramenyekana ubwoko bwabayeho hagati y'ubwoko bwa virusi, bwatumye ikwirakwira mu bantu; inzira yo kuyandura na yo iracyari kugenzurwa.
Bwana Ji na bagenzi be bavuze ko inzoka ari zo zafashe virusi kuva mu nyamaswa z'ibinyonyi zijya ku bantu, mu gihe zabaga ziri mu buryo bwo kongera guhuza ubwoko bumwe bwa poroteyine yitwa S.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abahanga mu bya siyansi bo mu Bushinwa bo mu mujyi wa Guangzhou, bwagaragaje ko ingona  inyamaswa zifite umunwa muremure zirya ibimonyo, zikunda gukoreshwa mu buvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa,  ari zo zishobora kuba ari zo zikingira SARS-CoV-2; ibyo bishingiye ku kuba ingona na SARS-CoV-2 bifite imiterere isa na 99%.
