Ibimenyetso by'umubiri n'ibya shimi bya SARS-CoV-2 biracyari ibidazwi.
Mu byiciro by'ibiro by'ubushakashatsi, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zishobora kubaho mu gihe cy'amasaha 48 mu bidukikije byumye no mu gihe cy'iminsi 5 ku bushyuhe buri munsi ya 20 °C na 4050 % y'ubushyuhe.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira imiterere nk'iyo.
SARS-CoV-2 izwiho kuba ishobora guhangana n'amashanyarazi ndetse no gushyushye kugeza kuri 56 °C mu gihe cy'iminota 30; ether, 75% ya ethyle alcohol, imiti yo guhanagura indwara irimo chlorine, aside ya perux, chlorophore n'ibindi bimenyetso by'amavuta bishobora kubuza virusi gukora neza, ariko chlorhexidine si ko ishobora kubikora.
Abantu muri rusange nta burinzi bafite ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2, bityo abantu bashobora kwandura iyi virusi nshya.
Kugeza ubu nta makuru y'ubushakashatsi bwimbitse bwakozwe ku buryo umubiri w'umuntu ugira icyo ukora ku ndwara ya SARS-CoV-2.
Bityo rero, dushobora kwerekeza gusa ku bushakashatsi bwa mbere ku zindi virusi za coronavirus, cyane cyane SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV (ishusho ya 4).4).
Ubusanzwe, virusi yinjiye mu mubiri w'umuntu, iba igaragajwe n'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri binyuze mu buryo bw'imiterere (ORP), harimo uburyo bwo kwakira C-type lectin, uburyo bwo kwakira Toll, uburyo bwo kwakira NOD n'uburyo bwo kwakira RIG-I.
