Ariko, kubera poroteyine ya N, SARS-CoV ishobora kwirinda igisubizo cy'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri.
Bidatinze, umubiri utangira guhangana na virusi.
T-Lymphocytes, harimo na T-CD4+ na CD8+, zifite uruhare runini mu kurinda umubiri.
Uturemangingo twa T twitwa CD4+ dutuma habaho udusimba tw'ubumara bwihariye mu turemangingo twa B, naho uturemangingo twa T twitwa CD8+ twica uturemangingo twanduye virusi.
T-helpers ikora sitokine ziterwa n'ubushye bukomeye, zigamije gufasha ingirabuzimafatizo.
Ariko kandi, koronavirusi ishobora kubuza ingirabuzimafatizo za T gukora, bigatuma zipfa nk'uko ziteganyijwe.
Ubwirinzi bwo mu mutwe, burimo ibice nka C3a na C5a, n'umubiri utanga ubudahangarwa, na bwo bufite uruhare runini mu kurwanya virusi.
Urugero, uduhimba tw'umubiri tw'umurwayi wari ukize, twafashije mu kugabanya MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, iyo abasoda b'umubiri batangiye gukora ibintu byinshi cyane, bituma habaho ingirabuzimafatizo nyinshi mu gace runaka, ibyo bikaba byangiza cyane ibihaha n'izindi ngingo, kandi mu mimerere mibi cyane, bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ubumuga bwinshi bw'umubiri, ndetse bikamuhitana.
Indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 ifite imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byinshi, ishobora gufata abantu bakuze bafite indwara zihuriyeho n'abagore batwite.
Abantu bafite virusi nyinshi cyangwa bafite ubumuga bwo mu mutwe, bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura.
Dukurikije ibisubizo by'ubushakashatsi ku bantu 425 ba mbere banduye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro cya SARS-CoV-2 kiri hagati y'umunsi umwe n'iminsi 14, cyane cyane iminsi 3.7.
Ariko kandi, ubushakashatsi ku bantu 1099 bwagaragaje ko igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro cyagendaga gitinda, ku kigereranyo, iminsi itatu, ariko ko cyagendaga gitinda hagati y'iminsi 0 na 24.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe nyuma y'aho, bushingiye ku mibare y'abantu 8.866 b'abanduye, bwagaragaje ko igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro cyari iminsi 4,8 (3,07,2).
Ni ngombwa ko inzego z'ubuzima zigena igihe cyo gushyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda, hagendewe ku gihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro, kugira ngo abantu batagira ibimenyetso batakwirakwizwa.
Abantu bose basanzwe bakoresha uburyo bwo kwirinda abantu banduye cyangwa bagiranye na virusi, bakamara iminsi 14 mu kato.
Ese igihe cyo guhagarika abantu kigomba kongerwa kugeza ku minsi 24?
Ibimenyetso by'ibanze bya COVID-19 akenshi ni ubushyuhe bukabije, bushobora kuba ari bwo bwonyine cyangwa bukaba buherekejwe n'ibindi bimenyetso, urugero nk'igisebe cyumye, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu myuniko, guhungabana, umutwe, ububabare mu ijosi, guhoberana, ububabare mu gatuza, guhoberana, kugira iseseme n'imvune.
Hari abarwayi bagiraga ubuhumekero n'ubuhumekero buke nyuma y'icyumweru batangiye kurwara.
Mu gihe indwara yari ikomeye, yagendaga yiyongera vuba, maze abarwayi bagatera indwara z'ubuhumekero, indwara yo guhungabana, indwara yo mu buryo bw'umubiri (acidose métabolique) n'indwara yo guhungabana (coagulopathy).
Abarwayi bafite umuriro mwinshi n'ibimenyetso by'indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero n'ubushye bukabije, bagomba kugenzurwa bakareba niba nta virusi ihari kugira ngo bashobore kubashyiramo ibipimo hakiri kare, kabone n'iyo baba badafite indwara z'ibihaha.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019, bwagaragaje ko 98% by'abarwayi bafite umuriro mwinshi, 76% bafite icyiho, 55% bafite ubuhuha, 3% bafite ibihaha; 8% by'abarwayi basabwaga guhumeka.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bubiri bwa vuba bwagaragaje ko abantu barwaye iyo ndwara mu muryango kandi ko bayandura ku bantu badafite ibimenyetso.
Ibisubizo bisa n'ibyo byabonetse mu mwaka wa 2012 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi ba MERS-CoV, bafite ibimenyetso by'ingenzi kandi ari ubushyuhe bukabije (98%), guhekenya (47%) no guhumeka nabi (55%).
Ariko 80% by'abo bantu basabwaga guhumeka, ni ukuvuga ko bari hejuru cyane ugereranyije n'abarwayi ba COVID-19, kandi bihuye n'umubare munini w'abapfa bazira MERS ugereranyije na COVID-19.
Abarwayi ba MERS na bo bagiraga igifu (26%) n'ububabare mu ijosi (21%).
Ibimenyetso by'ibanze by'abarwayi ba SARS ni ubushyuhe bukabije (99100 %), guhohoterwa (2975 %), guhumeka nabi (4042 %), gucibwamwo (2025 %) n'ububabare mu muhogo (1325 %), kandi 1420 % by'abarwayi basabwa guhumeka imyanya y'ubuhumekero.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare, umubare w'abapfuye ba COVID-19 wari 2%, naho umubare w'abamaze kwandura ku isi bose hamwe wari 66 576.
Ugereranyije n'ibyo, mu Ugushyingo 2002 SARS yari imaze guhitana abantu 10 ku ijana by'abamaze kwandura 8 096.
Ku kibazo cya MERS, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu kwezi kwa Kamena 2012 bwagaragaje ko abantu 37% bapfa muri abo bantu 2,494 banduye.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwagaragaje ko R0 ya SARS-CoV-2 yari 6,47 ku kigero cya 95% cy'icyizere (CI) kiri hagati ya 5,71 na 7,23, mu gihe R0 ya SARS-CoV yari hagati ya 2 na 4.
Kugereranya SARS-CoV-2 na MERS-CoV na SARA-CoV ku bijyanye n'ibimenyetso, igipimo cy'urupfu na R0 byatanzwe ku mbonerahamwe ya Table 1.1.
Ibi byerekana ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwiza kurusha MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV, ariko umubare w'abapfa iyo banduye virusi nshya uri hasi ugereranyije n'aba bombi ba mbere.
Bityo rero, kurwanya icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 bizakorohera cyane kurusha icyorezo cya MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV.
Akenshi, iyo umuntu yanduye mu muryango umwe cyangwa mu itsinda ry'abantu, baba bateraniye hamwe kubera impamvu runaka cyangwa bari kumwe mu modoka runaka, urugero nk'ubwato bw'urugendo.
Abarwayi bakunze kujya i Wuhan cyangwa mu tundi turere twatewe n'iki cyorezo, cyangwa bakahatura cyangwa bakaganira n'abanduye cyangwa abarwayi mu byumweru bibiri bya mbere y'uko batangira kurwara.
Ariko raporo z'ibanze zivuga ko abantu bashobora kuba bafite virusi nta bimenyetso byayo mu gihe kirenga ibyumweru bibiri, kandi abakize barangije kuva mu bitaro bashobora kongera kuyitwara, bikaba ari ikimenyetso cy'uko igihe cyo guhagarika abantu gishobora kongera.
Mu gihe cy'uburwayi bwa mbere, abarwayi baba bafite umubare usanzwe cyangwa wagabanutse w'amaraso y'ibanze (cyane cyane amarozi) mu maraso.
Urugero, abarwayi 1099 barwaye COVID-19 basanganywe imibare y'ibinyabuzima by'ibanze < 4×109/L, harimo imibare y'ibinyabuzima by'ibanze < 1×109/L, hamwe n'ubwiyongere bw'indwara ya asparagine-aminotransferase na virusemia.
Bamwe mu barwayi bagaragaje ko bafite imisemburo y'umura, imisemburo y'imitsi n'umuti w'amaraso, naho abenshi bagaragaje ko bafite C-reactive protein n'amaraso y'ibinyamushongo.
Mu barwayi barwaye cyane, D-dimer, igiterwa cyo gusenya fibrine mu maraso, yari hejuru, kandi umubare w'ingirabuzima fatizo za limfocyte wari ukomeje kugabanuka.
Abenshi mu barwayi ba COVID-19 bagaragaye indwara z'ibicurane ku mpande zombi cyangwa mu bihaha.
Abarwayi bakunze kugira indwara z'ibicurane, indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye n'izindi.
Iyo indwara y'ibicurane irangiye, indwara z'uburwayi zituma umuntu atabasha kugenzura neza imikorere y'umubiri, imyuka ihora yiyongera, kandi igatuma imikorere y'umubiri ihindagurika, bigatuma imikorere y'umwuka idakora neza.
Iyo udukoko tw'ibihaha tw'ubwoko bwa I na II tudakora neza, bituma udukoko tw'ibinyamushongo tutagira imbaraga kandi bigatuma udukoko tutagira imbaraga, bityo bigatuma uduhaha tudashobora kwagura kandi bigatuma duhomba.
Bityo rero, akenshi, ibipimo bibi cyane byo mu maradiyo y'amaradiyo bihuza n'iby'indwara zikomeye cyane.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, isuzuma rya mbere ry'indwara ya COVID-19 ryagaragaje ko ibice by'amaraso by'ibihaha by'umuntu, imiterere y'uruhu rw'ibinyabuzima (hyaline) n'imiterere y'imiterere y'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima (intertissue lymphocytic infiltration), kandi ko uturemangingo tw'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima twinshi mu bihaha by'abarwayi bapfuye bazize iyi ndwara, tuhuje n'indwara ziterwa na virusi n'indwara ya SARS, kandi ni kimwe n'izagaragaye mu barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Nk'icyemezo cy'ibanze mu gupima COVID-19, hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo kumenya SARS-CoV-2 RNA binyuze mu kwihinduranya kw'uruvange rwa polymerase hamwe na transcriptase (PCR hamwe na transcriptase).
Ariko, kubera ko ibipimo by'ibinyoma by'ibinyoma bishobora kwihutisha icyorezo, guhera ku itariki ya 13 Gashyantare 2020 mu Bushinwa batangiye gushyiraho ibipimo bishingiye ku bimenyetso by'ubuvuzi (ntibakirinda kwifashisha gusa PCR ifite transcriptase y'inyuma).
Ni na ko byagenze ku bantu basanganywe SARS.
Ku bw'ibyo, kugira ngo umuntu ashobore kumenya neza indwara ye, ni ngombwa ko ashyira hamwe amakuru y'ubuzima bwe, ibimenyetso by'indwara, ibipimo bya laboratwari n'ibyafashwe na radiographie.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ry'abahanga bayobowe na Bwana Feng Zhang basobanuye uburyo bwo gukoresha uburyo bwa SHERLOCK bushingiye ku gusubiramo CRISPR, mu kumenya SARS-CoV-2; ubwo buryo butuma haboneka ibice bya RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 byakozwe mu buryo bw'imiterere kuva kuri 20 × 1018 mol/l kugeza kuri 200 × 1018 mol/l (10100 copies kuri mikorolitiro y'igishushanyo cy'ibanze) hakoreshejwe imbonerahamwe mu gihe kitarenze isaha nta bikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga.
Ubu buryo bushya, nibushyira mu bikorwa neza ibipimo by'imiti, bushobora kuzamura cyane ubushobozi bwo gupima no koroshya uburyo bwo gupima.
Kubera ko nta buhanga buhari mu kurwanya coronavirus itari izwi, abaganga bashobora guha abarwayi ba COVID-19 ubuvuzi bwo kubungabunga gusa, ariko bagashaka gukoresha uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kuvura bwakoreshejwe cyangwa bwatanzwe mu kuvura izindi virusi za coronavirus, urugero nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, ndetse n'izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi (Umubare (Umubare 2).2).
Ubwo buryo bwo kuvura burimo cyangwa bushobora gukoreshwa harimo imiti igabanya ubukana bwa virusi, imiti igabanya ubwirinzi, imiti ya steroïde, plasma y'abarwayi bakize, imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa no gutanga ubufasha mu by'imitekerereze.
Hari n'abavugaga ko bashoboraga gukoresha amaraso y'abarwayi bari barakize.
Ibigo by'ubuvuzi biri mu nzira yo gukora udukoko tw'ubumara n'inkingo zo kurwanya virusi.
Mu byiciro by'ibanze, SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane cyane ibihaha, kandi ishobora no kuba ibasira ibindi bice byerekana ACE2, urugero nk'uruti rw'umugongo n'impyiko.
Nyamara, guhungabana no kunanirwa guhumeka ni byo byugarije abarwayi cyane kandi ni byo bibahitana.
Bityo rero, kugira ngo ibimenyetso bigabanuke no kurokora ubuzima, ni ngombwa cyane gushyigikira imikorere y'ubuhumekero, harimo imiti ya oksijeni rusange, gutanga oksijeni ifite ubushobozi bwinshi, guhumeka mu buryo butangiza umubiri no guhumeka mu bihaha mu buryo butangiza umubiri, bitewe n'uburemere bw'uburwayi.
