Byongeye kandi, gukomeza kubungabunga amazi n'umunyu, gukumira no kuvura indwara z'ubwandu n'isuri, no kurinda imikorere y'ingingo z'ingenzi ni iby'ingenzi ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2.
Byari bizwi ko ibicurane by'imiti biterwa n'uko abarwayi banduye virusi ya SARS na MERS bagira uburwayi bukabije.
Igitutu cy'imyakura ni uburyo bwo kwanduzanya mu buryo bwa sisitemu, bukorwa mu gusubiza ku cyiciro cy'imyakura, harimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ na MCP-1.
Izo sitokini zituma ingirabuzimafatizo z'umubiri zitera uturemangingo twinshi cyane tw'ibinyabuzima by'ubwigenge, ari na two dutera indwara z'imitsi y'amaraso n'uburwayi bwo mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
Mu kuvura cytocin storm, cyane cyane mu barwayi bafite ibibazo bikomeye, kurwanya ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ni ingenzi cyane.
Kugira ngo umuntu arwanye cytocin storm, yakoreshaga kortikosteroide na tocilisumab, ni ukuvuga uduhimba tw'umubiri tw'umubiri twitwa monoclonal antibodies, dukoreshwa mu kuvura interleukin-6.
Mu zindi nzira zo kuvura cytocin storm zishingiye ku kugabanya ubushobozi bw'ubwirinzi, harimo uburyo bwo kuvura ubwirinzi bugamije kugenzura T-insoro; kubuza cytocin IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF; guhagarika jenoside ya jenoside; gukoresha blinatumomab, suppresseurs cytocin signal 4 na inhibitors ya histone acetalase.
