Ahubwo bishobora guteza ingaruka zikomeye cyane cyane uburwayi bw'amagufa, kandi bigatuma umuntu atagira ubuzima bwiza.
Icyakora, imiti ya kortikosteroide mu gihe gito iri mu rugero ruto kandi ruciriritse, yagombye gukoreshwa mu buryo bw'ubwitonzi mu kuvura abarwayi ba COVID-19 bafite ibibazo bikomeye.
