Ariko, guterwa umuti wa remdesivir mu mitsi, nk'uko bimeze kuri nukleyotide, byagaragaye ko ari uburyo bwiza bwo kuvura umurwayi wo muri Amerika ufite COVID-19.
Remdecivir ni umuti uherutse gukorwa wo kurwanya virusi, watangiranye n'ikigo Gilead mu kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi za Ebola na Marburg.
Nyuma yaho, umuti wa remdesivir wagaragaje ko ushobora guhashya izindi virusi zifite urufunguzo rumwe rw'imiterere ya RNA, harimo na MERS na SARS.
Ishingiye kuri aya makuru, Gilead yahaye Ubushinwa uyu muti kugira ngo ukorerwe ubushakashatsi ku barwayi banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi ibyo bizatangazwa.
