Gufata amaraso y'abarwayi bakize indwara zandura, kugira ngo bavurwe n'abandi barwayi bafite iyo ndwara, cyangwa se kugira ngo barinde abaturage bafite amagara mazima, byatangiye kera cyane.
Mu by'ukuri, abarwayi bakize akenshi baba bafite ingano yo hejuru y'abakora antibodies mu maraso yabo kugira ngo barwanye pathogen.
Imiti igwanya indwara iba mu mubiri wa B-lymphocyte, ikora imyanya itandukanye yo kurwanya indwara, kandi ikamenya molekile zimwe na zimwe z'imiti igwanya indwara, ikanazica.
Hashingiwe kuri iyi ngengabitekerezo, plasma yavanywe mu maraso y'abarwayi bakize COVID-19 maze ishyirwa mu barwayi 10 barwaye cyane.
Mu masaha 24 gusa, ibimenyetso byabo byari byarazamutse, ubukana bw'ubwugarizi n'umurimo wa virusi byagabanutse, kandi amaraso yabo yari afite umwuka wa ogisijeni.
