Hakenewe kuvugurura ibipimo by'ubushakashatsi ku bantu bakekwaho indwara ya COVID-19 n'abafashwe
Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryashyize ahagaragara igitabo gito cy'ibanze cy'ubuvuzi n'ubuvuzi bw'ubwandu bushya bwa coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV), kirimo amakuru y'ubunararibonye twabonye kandi gitanga inama z'ingirakamaro zo kurwanya iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Ariko icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara nshya, bityo gusobanukirwa no kumenya byagiye byiyongera buhoro buhoro dushingiye ku byavuye mu bushakashatsi n'ubushakashatsi; bityo, uburyo bwo gupima no kuvura na bwo bwagiye buhinduka.
Muri iyi baruwa, twashubije igitekerezo kimwe ku bijyanye n'inama zacu, kandi dutanga ibipimo bishya by'ubushakashatsi ku bantu bakekwaho uburwayi n'abamaze kwemezwaho uburwayi, dukurikije inyandiko y'ibanze y'ibanze y'ibanze y'ubushakashatsi n'ubuvuzi ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 (Version ya karindwi) yatanzwe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya RDC.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, habonetse icyorezo cya coronavirus nshya 2019 (2019-nCoV), ubu cyitwa coronavirus infection 2019 (COVID-19), kandi iyi ndwara yiswe severe acute respiratory syndrome 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yashyize ahagaragara COVID-19 nk'icyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 itsinda ryacu ryakoze igitabo gito cy'ubufasha cyasohotse kuri interineti ku rubuga rwa Military Medical Research ku itariki ya 6 Gashyantare 2020.
Icyo gitabo cyakwirakwijwe cyane.
Twagombye kuzirikana ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, bityo gusobanukirwa no kumenya byagiye byiyongera buhoro buhoro dushingiye ku byavuye mu bushakashatsi n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe; bityo, uburyo bwo gupima no kuvura na bwo bwagiye buhinduka.
Urugero, kuva ku itariki ya 16 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, hasohotse impapuro ndwi z'ibiro by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye byita ku buzima (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), zanditseho "Icyemezo cyo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19", kandi zimwe mu ngingo z'iyo nyandiko zarahindutse cyane.
Mu nyandiko iherutse gutangwa na Zhou hamwe n'abandi banditsi, hari amagambo yavuzwe ku nama zacu, harimo inama zoroshye zo gusuzuma indwara zishingiye ku buhanga bw'abaganga.
Iki gikorwa cyongereye ku nama zacu ubuhamya bushya bw'ingirakamaro, ndetse gitanga n'amakuru y'ingirakamaro y'ibanze kuri iki cyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Turemeza ko umurimo wabo ufite agaciro kandi turabashimira.
Ariko kandi, hakurikijwe ibitabo biherutse gusohoka byitwa "Inama z'ibanze z'ubushakashatsi n'ubuvuzi ku cyorezo cya COVID-19" (ingingo ya karindwi y'igeragezwa) n'ibisubizo by'ubushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa, ibyo byose bikeneye kuvugururwa.
Dukurikije inyandiko ya karindwi y 'iri tangazo (y'itariki ya 3 Werurwe 2020), kugira ngo hakorwe isesengura ryimbitse mu gihe hemejwe ikibazo cy 'ukukekwa indwara, hagomba guhuzwa kimwe mu bintu by'amateka y 'indwara n 'ibimenyetso bibiri by 'indwara:
Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) amateka y'urugendo cyangwa aho waba uri mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu nkengero zawo cyangwa mu tundi turere tw'abaturage aho habonetse abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bigaragara; (2) amateka y'abahuye n'abarwayi banduye SARS-CoV-2 (bafite ibipimo bishingiye kuri aside ya nukleyini); (3) amateka y'abahuye n'abarwayi bafite umuriro mwinshi cyangwa bafite ibimenyetso byo guhumeka baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu nkengero zawo cyangwa mu tundi turere tw'abaturage aho habonetse abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bigaragara; (4) amateka y'abahuye n'amatsinda y'abantu bafite indwara zemejwe (≥ 2 y'abarwayi bafite umuriro mwinshi cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero byanditswe mu gihe cy'ibyumweru 2 mu mazu mato, amashuri, ibiro n'ibindi.
Ibimenyetso by'indwara: (1) ubushyuhe bukabije n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka; (2) ibimenyetso by'inyuma by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) umubare w'ibinyugunyugu wa leukoti usanzwe cyangwa wagabanutse, ufite umubare w'ibinyugunyugu wagabanutse mu gihe cy'ibimenyetso.
Gushyiraho icyemezo cy'indwara y'umuntu wemejwe ko arwaye bigomba gushingira ku kuba umuntu akekwaho indwara afite kimwe mu bimenyetso bikurikira by'indwara ziterwa n'imiterere y'umubiri cyangwa se se ya virusi, ni ukuvuga: (1) gupima PCR mu gihe nyacyo byerekana ko SARS-CoV-2 ari yo yandura; (2) gupima virusi mu buryo bwuzuye bigaragaza ko ifite homogeni nyinshi ku ndwara z'ubwoko bushya; (3) gupima virusi byerekana ko IgM na IgG by'indwara ziterwa na SARS-CoV-2 ari byo byerekana ko virusi ari yo yandura; cyangwa guhindura IgG byerekana ko SARS-CoV-2 ari yo yandura, cyangwa se kongera inshuro 4 ku bipimo by'indwara ziterwa na fazole ugereranyije n'ibimenyetso by'indwara ziterwa na SARS-CoV-2.
Birashoboka kandi ko mu cyiciro cya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020) cy'iyi nyandiko, hakongewemo ibipimo bya PCR mu gihe nyacyo ku byerekeye aside ya nukleyini mu nzira zo guhumeka cyangwa mu bipimo by'amaraso.
Gupima indwara ziterwa n'ibinyabutabire by'amaraso byongerewe mu bitabo bya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) no mu bya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); hanyuma mu bitabo bya karindwi hakongerwaho ikenewe cy'ibimenyetso bya serolojiya.
Ayo mavugurura ashingiye ku bikorwa by'ubushakashatsi byakozwe n'abashakashatsi mu gushaka uburyo bwiza bwo kumenya aside ya nukleyini mu gihe cyo gusuzuma indwara vuba, no gusuzuma ibipimo biva mu nzira z'ubuhumekero, harimo no gutoranya amaraso, bituma haboneka ibipimo bitandukanye kandi bigatuma haboneka ibisubizo by'ibizamini by'indwara zihariye mu byemeza indwara.
Icyakora, hari ibimenyetso byinshi bigaragaza ko abantu bafite ibimenyetso bidasanzwe n'abatabifite bagomba kwitabwaho mu buryo bwitondewe.
Bityo rero, ikarita y'inzira igaragaza ibyabaye mu bushakashatsi bwa Zhou n'abandi, yagombye kuvugururwa, kubera ko abantu badafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi bashyirwa mu itsinda ry'abantu bafite ibyago bike byo kurwara.
Nanone kandi, hari ibintu byinshi bigomba gusobanurwa mu gihe cy'imikorere y'abaganga n'ubushakashatsi.
Mu gusoza, turasaba ko twakwizera ko tuzabona ibimenyetso by'ukuri, kandi turasaba abasomyi bacu gutanga ibitekerezo byabo.
Ku bijyanye no kumenya uko umuntu yakora 'abatekereza ko arwaye' n'uko yakora 'abamaze kwemezwa' turasaba abasomyi gukurikiza amabwiriza agezweho mu bihugu batuyemo.
Itsinda ryacu kandi rizakomeza kuvugurura inama z'uko ryafasha mu buryo bw'ingirakamaro.
Bangladesh yatangaje abantu batanu bashya bishwe na COVID-19  umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye ku munsi
Ejo, Bangladesh yemeje abantu bashya batanu bapfuye bishwe na COVID-19 ku munsi umwe.
Ni umubare munini w'abantu bishwe na virusi mu munsi umwe.
