Umuryango w'Isi Yose wita ku Buzima watangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyugarije isi
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubwandu ya COVID-19, iterwa na koronavirusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" rigaragaza gusa ubukana bw'iki cyorezo aho kugaragaza akaga k'ubwandu, OMS ivuga ko leta z'ibihugu zikeneye gufata ingamba zikurikira:
Ibihugu byose hamwe biracyafite ubushobozi bwo kugira uruhare mu iterambere ry'icyorezo.
Ibi birashoboka mu gihe ibihugu byashyizeho ingufu mu kumenya, gupima, kuvura, gushyira abantu mu kato, gukurikirana igihe indwara itangiye, no guhuza abaturage babo, nk'uko byasobanuwe n'Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Bwana Tedros Adán Hebreisus.
"Turahangayikishijwe cyane n'ubwiyongere buteye ubwoba bw'iki cyorezo n'ukuntu cyagaragaye, ndetse n'ukuntu nta cyo twakora".
Dr Tom Friedan, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, yavuze ko iki cyorezo "kitari cyigeze kibaho".
Mu kiganiro yagiranye na CNN muri Gashyantare, yavuze ko nta virusi yindi y'ubuhumekero itari grippe yari yarigeze igaragara kuva yatangira kugeza aho ikwirakwira ku isi yose.
Bwana Gebreyesus yavuze ibintu nk'ibyo, avuga ko tutigeze tubona icyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus.
Nta n'ubwo twigeze tubona icyorezo cyakwirakwira mu buryo bufite ubushobozi bwo kugenzurwa.
Mu kwezi kwa mbere, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu bw'abaturage ku rwego mpuzamahanga, nyuma yaho ikagiha icyiciro gishya cya pandemic.
Dr. Anthony Fauci, umuyobozi w'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Indwara z'Akarwara n'Amasuzuguro, yavuze ko iki cyorezo ari "intangiriro gusa, ko kizagenda kirushaho kuba kibi".
