Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 20192020  ni icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na Coronavirus y'indwara ikomeye yo guhumeka- 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Iki cyorezo cyamenyekanye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa mu Ukuboza 2019, ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama 2020 hatangajwe ko hari ikibazo cy'ubukungu bw'abaturage ku rwego mpuzamahanga, nyuma yaho ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020 cyemezwa ko ari icyorezo.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, mu bihugu 210 no mu turere twaho, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 1,61 bari baranduye COVID-19, bituma hapfa abantu bagera ku 97.000.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 barakize.
