Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe, kandi abantu bamwe na bamwe banduye bashobora kwanduzwa n'iyo ndwara nta bimenyetso bafite.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara cyane ni ubushyuhe bukabije (88%) n'inkorora (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara harimo umunaniro, gutakaza umwuka, kubura impumuro, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu myuniko no mu ngingo, kuribwa mu muhogo, kuribwa umutwe, guhohoterwa, gucibwamwo, gutakaza amaraso, gucibwamwo cyangwa cyanosis.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga ibimenyetso byihutirwa nk'ububabare bwo guhumeka, ububabare buhoraho cyangwa kumva ko umutima uhagaze mu gatuza, kumva utunguwe mu buryo butunguranye, guhangayika mu gihe uhagurutse, no kugira ubururu mu maso cyangwa mu kanwa. Iyo ibimenyetso bibayeho, ugomba gushaka ubufasha bw'abaganga.
Hari abantu bashobora kuba barwaye indwara nta bimenyetso bafite, ariko ibipimo byerekana ko bayanduye, bityo abaganga bagasaba ko abantu bagirana imishyikirano ya bugufi n'abarwayi bagaragaweho indwara bakagenzurwa cyane kandi bakagenzurwa kugira ngo barebe ko banduye.
