Uburyo bwo kurwanya icyorezo harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara, kuzirwanya cyangwa kuzirinda.
Gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara bikorwa mu bihe bya mbere kandi bigamije gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abanduye, kandi bikubiyemo izindi ngamba zo kugenzura ubwandu no gukingira kugira ngo bareke ikwirakwira ry'iyi ndwara mu baturage.
Mu gihe nta bushobozi bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo, hashyirwaho ingamba zo kugabanya ingaruka: ingamba zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo no kugabanya ingaruka ku rwego rw'ubuzima n'abaturage.
Ingamba zo gukumira no kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo zishobora gufatwa icyarimwe.
Gukumira ubwandu bisaba ingamba zikomeye cyane zo guhindura icyorezo, ugabanya umubare w'abanduye hasi ya 1. Kimwe mu byo dukora mu kugenzura icyorezo cy'indwara zandura ni uguhagarika icyorezo, bizwi nka Epidemic Equalization.
Iyo mihati igabanya ibyago byo kurengera ubuzima bw'abantu, kandi ikaduha igihe gihagije cyo gukora inkingo n'ubuvuzi.
Ibipimo bitari ibiyobyabwenge bishobora gufasha guhangana n'iki cyorezo birimo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nko kugira isuku y'amaboko, gukoresha udupfukamunwa no kwigunga; ingamba zo mu rwego rw'abaturage zigamije gutandukanya abantu, nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika ibikorwa by'abantu benshi; gushishikariza abaturage gufasha no kugira uruhare muri ibyo bikorwa; hamwe n'ingamba zo kubungabunga ibidukikije, nko gusukura imiterere. Nyuma y'uko mu Bushinwa ubukana bw'iki cyorezo bwigaragaje, hafashwe ingamba zikomeye zo kugabanya iki cyorezo, nko gufunga imijyi yose no gushyiraho gahunda zikomeye zo kwirinda ingendo.
Ibindi bihugu na byo byafashe ingamba zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hatangijwe gahunda yo gupima abantu benshi no gushyiraho gahunda zo kwirinda mu gace runaka, kandi hashyizweho uburyo bwo kubamenyesha ko abantu banduye bagiye cyangwa bagiye.
Singapore yatanze inkunga y'amafaranga ku bantu banduye bari mu mwiherero, kandi yashyizeho amande menshi ku batayashyizeho.
Muri Tayiwani, kongeramo ibikoresho byo kwivuza no gufatira ibihano abantu bafite imiti myinshi, mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika, hagaragaye ko hari ibibazo bikomeye byo kugabanya (kugabanya ariko kudakomeza icyorezo) no kucyimya (kugabanya icyorezo).
Gushyiraho politiki nziza yo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara bishobora kugabanya ibiro by'ubuzima ku kigero cya 2/3, kandi bigatuma abantu bapfa bigabanyukaho kabiri, ariko bigatuma abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana bapfa, kandi bigatuma imibereho y'abantu irushaho kuzamba.
Gucika indwara bishobora kuba uburyo bwiza, ariko bigomba gukoreshwa mu gihe virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu baturage (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rwarakozwe, niba ari mbere yaho), kuko bitabaye ibyo, ikwirakwira ry'indwara rizasubira vuba igihe ingamba zizakurwaho.
Gufata ingamba z'igihe kirekire zo guhashya icyorezo bitera ingaruka ku bukungu no ku mibereho y'abaturage.
Kugeza ubu nta miti yemewe yo kuvura COVID-19, ariko hari ibikorwa byo kuyikoresha harimo no kugerageza imiti isanzwe.
Kujya mu bitaro by'abarwayi ba virusi itera ibicurane, kunywa amazi ahagije no kuruhuka bishobora kugufasha kugabanya ibimenyetso bya virusi itera ibicurane.
Bitewe n'uburemere bw'uburwayi, umurwayi ashobora gukenera ko bamuha umwuka wa ogisijeni, bakamuha amazi mu maraso, kandi bakamufasha guhumeka.
Gukoresha imiti ya siteroyide bishobora gusa kugira ingaruka mbi.
Imyinshi mu miti yari imaze kwemerwa kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi, nayo iri gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS kandi yatangaje ko hari imiti isanzwe n'indi yo mu rugo ishobora koroshya ibimenyetso biterwa na SARS-CoV-19.
OMS ivuga ko kongera ubushobozi no guhuza ubuzima bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 ari byo by'ibanze mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) n'ibiro by'akarere by'umuryango w'abibumbye byita ku buzima (OMS) byasohoye amabwiriza agenga amavuriro n'inzego z'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze mu rwego rwo gufasha mu kongera gukwirakwiza umutungo ku byiciro byinshi, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu gupima COVID-19, guhagarika ibikorwa by'ubutabazi mu gihe bishoboka, kumenya virusi no gutandukanya abarwayi bafite icyorezo cya COVID-19, no kwagura ubushobozi bwo kuvura cyane binyuze mu kwigisha abakozi no kongera ibikoresho bya virusi itera SIDA n'imyanya yo kuryamamo.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku birebana n'aho umuntu wa mbere wanduye indwara yitwa "umurwayi wa zeru" ashobora kuba yaraturutse.
Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko yanduye coronavirus nshya, ashobora kuba yaranduye mu kwezi k'Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi, umubare w'abandura coronavirus mu ntara ya Hubei wari ukomeje kwiyongera.
Byinshi byabaga bifitanye isano n'isoko rya Huanan ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja, aho kandi hagurishwaga inyamaswa nzima, kandi imwe mu nyigisho ni uko virusi yinjiye mu mubiri w'umuntu iturutse kuri imwe muri izo nyamaswa; mu yandi magambo, virusi ifite inkomoko ya zoonosis. Ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, mu bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei, hagiye haboneka indwara y'uburwayi bw'ibicurane by'ubwoko butaramenyekana, yakoreweho n'umuganga witwa Zhang Tianjin, kuri uyu wa 27 Ukuboza, yamenyesheje ikigo cya Jianghan cyo kugenzura no gukumira indwara mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru by'i Wuhan baburiye bagenzi babo ku byerekeye virusi ya corona isa na SARS.
Abaganga umunani muri bo, barimo na Li Wenlian, bahawe umuburo n'abapolisi ko bagomba kuryozwa gukwirakwiza ibihuha, naho umuganga witwa Ai Feng, yahawe igihano n'abayobozi be kubera ko yatumye abantu bagira ubwoba.
Nyuma yaho, ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza, Komisiyo y'Umutekano mu Mujyi wa Wuhan yashyize ahagaragara itangazo ry'uko iki kibazo cyabayeho, maze imenyesha OMS.
Inzego z'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan zatangaje ko hari abantu benshi banduye indwara ya Pneumonia itaramenyekana, ku buryo byasabye ko hatangira iperereza mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa mbere.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze no mu zindi ntara z'Ubushinwa, byatewe n'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'Ubushinwa ndetse n'uko Wuhan ari umuhanda w'imodoka n'umuhanda wa gari ya moshi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwatangaje ko abantu bashya 140 banduye mu munsi umwe, barimo babiri mu mujyi wa Beijing n'undi umwe mu mujyi wa Shenzhen.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu makuru ya nyuma, ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020, abantu 6 174 bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso by'iyi ndwara. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zarenze u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani mu kuba ari zo zifite umubare munini w'abanduye iyi ndwara ku isi. Ku itariki ya 9 Mata 2020, ku isi hose, abantu barenga miliyoni 1.61 bari bamaze kwandura iyi ndwara, abantu barenga 97.000 barapfuye, abandi barenga 364.000 barakira.
Ibihugu n'uturere bigera kuri 200 byiboneye nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo, ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza rw'abantu no gushyiraho amabwiriza yo kugenzura imipaka.
Ingamba z'igihugu zo guhangana na virusi ya Corona harimo guhagarika ikwirakwira ryayo, nko guhagarika abantu (bimwe mu bizwi nka Guma mu Rugo, gufunga abantu mu ngo cyangwa kwigunga), no gushyiraho amasaha y'umukwabu. Kugeza ku wa 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abaturage ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, bari mu buryo runaka bwo kwigunga, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari mu kato muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 bari mu kato muri Afurika y'Epfo, n'abantu bagera kuri miliyari 1.3 mu Buhinde.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi hose bari mu buryo runaka bwo gufungirwa mu ngo zabo, maze nyuma y'iminsi ibiri uwo mubare wiyongera ugera kuri miliyari 2.6  hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko arwaye COVID-19 yabonetse i Wuhan ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019; hari indi raporo itaragenzurwa ivuga ko ari ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, umuganga witwa Zhang Jissian yakoraga ku muntu wari warwaye indwara y'uburwayi bw'ibicurane by'ubwoko butaramenyekana, ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza, ikigo cye cyamenyesheje Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara cya Jianghan mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Ibipimo bya mbere by'imiterere y'abarwayi byabaye ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza 2019, byagaragaje ko hari virusi ya SARS.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza, Komisiyo y'Umutekano mu Mujyi wa Wuhan yashyize ahagaragara itangazo rivuga ko iki cyorezo cyakomeje kwiyongera.
Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS) wabimenyeshejwe kuri uwo munsi.
Kubera ibyo bimenyetso, polisi yaburiye abaganga bo muri Wuhan ko bagomba kuryozwa gukwirakwiza ibihuha by'uko iki cyorezo cyadutse.
Mu mizo ya mbere, Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yavuze ko nta bimenyetso bifatika byerekana ko virusi nshya ishobora gukwirakwira ku bantu.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukomeye bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi, nyuma y'aho iyo virusi yaje kwitwa "Intambara y'Abaturage" n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa, Xi Jinping.
Ibintu byatangiye kugenda neza mu mateka y'abantu, tariki ya 23 Mutarama hatangajwe ko hazabaho uruzitiro rw'isuku, abantu bakaba batemerewe kwinjira mu mujyi wa Wuhan, nyuma y'aho, icyo cyemezo cyakwirakwijwe mu mijyi 15 yo mu ntara ya Hubei, kigira ingaruka ku bantu bagera kuri miliyoni 57.
Mu mujyi, imodoka z'abantu ku giti cyabo ntizemerewe gukoreshwa.
Mu duce twinshi, iminsi mikuru yo kwizihiza Umwaka Mushya w'Abashinwa (itariki ya 25 Mutarama) yahagaritswe.
Nanone kandi, abategetsi batangaje ko bagiye kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo by'i Huoshenshang, bikaba byarangiye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hubatswe ikindi bitaro, ari cyo Leishenshan, cyakira abandi barwayi.
Usibye ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa kandi bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 i Wuhan, nk'ibigo by'inama n'ibibuga by'imikino, mu bitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yafashe ingamba z'inyongera zo gukumira icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga impapuro z'ubuzima ku bantu bakora ingendo no kongera igihe cyo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa.
Muri icyo gihugu hose, kaminuza n'amashuri byafunzwe.
Akarere ka Hong Kong na Macau kafashe ingamba zitandukanye, cyane cyane ku mashuri na za kaminuza.
Mu turere twinshi tw'u Bushinwa, abategetsi bashyizeho uburyo bwo gukora mu ibanga.
Mu ntara ya Hubei no hanze yayo, hatowe amategeko yo guca abantu mu ngendo.
Amasaha y'urugendo rw'abantu bose yahinduwe, kandi amazu ndangamurage yo mu Bushinwa yose yafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Mu mijyi myinshi hashyizweho gahunda yo kugenzura urujya n'uruza rw'abaturage, kandi byemezwa ko abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bahanganye n'uburyo runaka bwo guhagarika urujya n'uruza rw'abantu hanze. Nyuma y'uko iki cyorezo cyatangiye gukwirakwira ku isi muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda ko virusi ivanwa mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, i Beijing hashyizweho iminsi 14 y'igihango cyo gusezerera abantu bose bakora ingendo mpuzamahanga binjira mu mujyi. Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, mu Bushinwa hari hamaze kugaragara umuntu umwe gusa wanduye mu gihugu, mu minsi itanu mbere yaho, uyu muntu akaba yaturutse i Guangzhou avuye i Istanbul.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa, Li Keqiang, yatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'uburwayi buturuka mu gihugu ryarangiye, kandi ko icyorezo cy'uburwayi mu Bushinwa cyafashwe.
Kuri uwo munsi, ingamba zo kujya i Hubei usibye Wuhan zakuriweho, nyuma y'amezi abiri intara ifunze kubera gufungwa. Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko kuva ku ya 28 Werurwe, kwinjira ku bantu bafite viza cyangwa uruhushya rwo gutura bizasubikwa.
Abashaka kuza mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula z'u Bushinwa.
Ku ya 30 Werurwe, leta y'Ubushinwa yasabye inganda no mu nganda kongera gukora, kandi iha ibigo inkunga y'amafaranga. Ku ya 4 Mata saa kumi za mu gitondo habaye iminota itatu yo guceceka, itangiza umunsi wo gupfusha abantu bishwe na coronavirus watangajwe n'inama ya leta, ukaba uhuza n'umunsi mukuru wa Quinminh, ariko leta y'u Bushinwa yasabye abaturage guhimbaza abahitanywe na COVID-19 ku buryo bwa interineti, bakurikiza amabwiriza yo gutandukanya abantu kugira ngo hatongera kubaho icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Byemejwe ko COVID-19 yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020 iturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ubuzima y'Igihugu yatangaje ko umubare w'abamaze kwandura iyi ndwara wiyongereye cyane, ahanini bitewe n'uko abantu benshi bari baje i Tagu bakurikiza idini rishya ryitwa Shinchonjji Church of Jesus.
Abayoboke ba Shinchonji baje i Tegu baturutse i Wuhan, bivugwa ko ari ho habereye icyo cyorezo.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9,336 ba Kiliziya, 1,261 (hagati ya 13%) batangaje ko bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara.
Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, muri Koreya hagezweho abantu barenga 2.000 banduye, naho ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare, uwo mubare wariyongereye ugera ku bantu 3.150.
Ibigo bya gisirikare byose bya Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu basuzumwe bagaragaza ko banduye virusi.
Iki cyorezo cyagize ingaruka ku ngendo, bityo gahunda z'indege za sosiyete z'indege zahindutse. Koreya y'Epfo yatangije gahunda yo gupima abaturage kugira ngo barebe ko banduye virusi, gukurikirana abo bahuye no gushyiraho ingamba zo gushyira abantu mu kato. Iyi gahunda ifatwa nk'iyari nini kandi nziza mu rwego rw'ishami ryayo ku isi.
Uburyo bwo gupima harimo kubwira abantu bose bavuye mu mahanga ibimenyetso byabo binyuze kuri porogaramu ya telefoni, gupima virusi ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kwagura ubushobozi bwo gupima kugeza ku bantu 20,000 buri munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo yafashwe nk'iy'ibanze mu kurwanya iki cyorezo, nubwo nta mijyi yose yahagaritswe.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zishimagiza ibyo perezida yakoze cyangwa basaba ko Bwana Muno yafungwa kubera ko batekereza ko uburyo leta yabyitwayemo mu guhangana n'icyorezo atari bwo bwiza.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Korea y'Epfo yabonye umubare muto w'abanduye ku munsi umwe mu byumweru bine.
Tariki 29 Werurwe, hatangajwe ko guhera tariki ya 1 Mata, abimukira bose bavuye mu mahanga bazajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko itangazamakuru ryabitangaje, ku itariki ya 1 Mata, ibihugu 121 byasabye Koreya y'Epfo ubufasha mu gupima virusi.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Irani yatangaje ko abantu ba mbere banduye SARS-CoV-2 mu mujyi wa Qum, aho Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi bw'Ubuvuzi yavuze ko abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma y'aho kuri uwo munsi.
Ingamba za mbere zafashwe na leta harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'indi mirimo y'umuco n'imikino, amasengesho yo ku wa gatanu, ndetse no gufunga kaminuza, amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yatanze miriyari eshanu za rials mu kurwanya virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yatangaje ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko leta itazateganya gushyira mu kato uturere twose twugarijwe n'iki cyorezo, ahubwo ko abantu ku giti cyabo ari bo bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Muri Werurwe, hatangajwe gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imigi, ariko abantu bakomeje kugenda cyane hagati y'imigi mbere y'Umunsi Mukuru w'Abaperesi.
Ibibanza byera by'Abashia i Qum byari byuguruye ku bantu bajya gusengera Imana kugeza ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Mu gihe hari ibirego by'uko iki cyorezo cyabaye muri Irani, ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare ibihugu birenga icumi byari byaravuze ko byibasiye Irani, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko iki cyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha 388 byibasiye leta ya Irani kugeza kuri iyo tariki.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, kandi ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, 23 mu banyamuryango bayo 290 basuzumwe basanga bafite virusi.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch (Ku murinzi w'uburenganzira bwa muntu) yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura byimazeyo abarwanashyaka b'uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe bazira ibitekerezo byabo bitemewe, ndetse no kurekura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zihuje n'icyo cyiciro.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima rivuga ko hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwiza virusi mu bigo by'imiryango byugarijwe n'abantu benshi, urugero nk'amabohero, aho usanga nta buvuzi buhagije buboneka.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bishwe n'iki cyorezo mu munsi umwe, ni ukuvuga umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye kuva iki cyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 ba Iran n'abategetsi ba leta bapfuye bazize iyo ndwara.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, muri Irani buri saha habonetse abantu 50 bashya banduye coronavirus, kandi buri minota icumi hapfa umuntu umwe kubera coronavirus.
Umuvugizi wa OMS yavuze ko umubare w'abandura muri Irani ushobora kuba uri hejuru inshuro eshanu ugereranyije n'ibyavuzwe ku rwego rw'ubutegetsi.
Hari kandi n'ibitekerezo ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'igihugu mu by'ubukungu bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Komiseri Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku burenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu bigabanywa ku bihugu byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama, byemejwe ko iyi ndwara yageze mu Butaliyani, ubwo abashyitsi babiri b'Abashinwa bapimwe SARS-CoV-2 mu mujyi wa Roma, bagasanga ari bo bayanduye.
Umubare w'abandura watangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose zijya mu Bushinwa no kuva mu Bushinwa, ndetse itangaza ko ari mu bihe by'ubukungu bwihuse.
Nyuma yaho, habonetse itsinda ry'abantu batandukanye banduye COVID-19. Byose byatangiye ubwo habonekaga abantu 16 banduye mu karere ka Lombardy ku ya 21 Gashyantare. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yasohoye itegeko rishya ryo kugabanya icyorezo, ryashyize abantu barenga 50,000 mu mirenge 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani mu kato.
Minisitiri w'intebe Giuseppe Conte yavuze ko kwinjira no gusohoka mu karere kagerwaho n'icyorezo bizakurwaho.
Ku itariki ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'u Butaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza bifungwa kubera ko icyo gihe mu Butaliyani hamaze gupfa abantu 100.
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo n'imikino ya shampiyona ya A, yagombaga kuba inyuma y'imiryango ifungiye kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose y'imikino yigijwe inyuma nibura ukwezi kumwe.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse guhagarika ibikorwa byose by'ubucuruzi no gufunga ibigo by'ubucuruzi uretse amaduka manini n'amafasiporo. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani cy'ubuvuzi, ubuvuzi, ubutabazi n'ubuvuzi bw'indembe (SIAARTI) cyashyize ahagaragara inama z'imyitwarire y'ubuvuzi ku bijyanye na porotokaramu zo gushyiraho umurongo wo gufasha abarwayi, bishobora kuba ngombwa ko bashyirwaho.
Ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwirutse Ubushinwa mu gupfa kubera coronavirus, buza ku mwanya wa mbere ku isi nyuma yo gutangaza ko abantu 3,405 bapfuye.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, byamenyekanye ko u Burusiya bwohereje mu Butaliyani indege icyenda z'intambara zitwaye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari abantu 128,948 bamaze kwandura coronavirus, hapfuye abantu 15,887 naho abakize haboneka abantu 21,815, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo imwe ya CNN ivuga ko umubare munini w'abapfa mu Butaliyani ushobora kuba utewe n'impamvu ebyiri  umubare munini w'abageze mu za bukuru muri icyo gihugu no kutabona uburyo bwo gupima abantu bose bafite coronavirus muri iki gihe.
Ubwongereza bwitabiriye iyi virusi buhoro cyane kurusha ibindi bihugu byose byahuye n'icyo cyorezo, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'u Bwongereza ntiyigeze isaba abaturage kubahiriza uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo gutandukanya abantu cyangwa gushyira mu kato.
Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatanze itangazo rigira riti: "Tugomba kwirinda ingendo zose n'imikoranire idakenewe, tugasaba abantu gukora mu rugo igihe cyose bishoboka, tukirinda ahantu hahurira abantu benshi nko mu tubari, muri resitora no mu mazu y'imyidagaduro".
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, leta yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro, nk'utubari n'amakipe y'imikino, bigomba gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi isezeranya abaturage bakora ko bazishyura kugeza kuri 80% by'umushahara wabo, ariko ntibarenze £2,500 ku kwezi nk'ingamba zo gushyigikira abaturage mu gihe cy'ibibazo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, minisitiri w'intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo gutandukanya abantu, abuza abantu guhurira hamwe barenga babiri, kandi agabanya ingendo no kuruhuka mu kirere gusa mu bihe by'ingorabahizi.
Mu buryo butandukanye n'ingamba zabanje, izo ngamba zashyizweho hakoreshejwe polisi, gucibwa amande no kwirukana abantu benshi.
Ibigo byinshi byategetswe gufunga, usibye ibigo by'ubucuruzi byita ku buzima bw'abaturage, harimo amasupamaketi, farumasi, banki, amaduka y'ubucuruzi, sitasiyo z'ibikomoka kuri peteroli n'amagaraji.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, mu ntara ya Washington mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bw'inyanja ya Pasifika, umugabo wari watashye avuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama, yemejwe ko ari we muntu wa mbere wa mbere wafashwe na COVID-19.
Tariki 29 Mutarama, mu nzu y'Umurenge wa White House hashyizweho itsinda ry'abakozi rigamije kurwanya coronavirus.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubutegetsi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko mu rwego rw'ubuzima rusange hari ikibazo cy'ubukungu bw'ikiremwamuntu, ndetse buhagarika ingendo z'abaturuka mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara, ikigo cya leta cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima rusange, cyatangaje ko cyateguye igikoresho cyacyo cyo gupima.
Nubwo bimeze bityo, ibipimo by'abatuye Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ntibyatangiye guhita, bityo ingaruka z'uko icyorezo cyateye muri icyo gihe zagiye zihishwa.
Gupima byagorwaga n'uko hari hataraboneka ibyangombwa by'ubushakashatsi byatanzwe na leta muri Gashyantare, kuba nta ruhushya rwa leta rwari rufite rwo gukoresha ibyangombwa bitari ibya leta, byakozwe n'ibigo by'ubushakashatsi, ibigo bitandukanye n'amavuriro, ndetse no kuba nta n'ibisabwa byariho mbere ya Werurwe byatumaga abaturage bapimwa (byashoboraga gukorwa gusa ku mabwiriza y'umuganga wabaga abarwayi).
The Washington Post yatangaje ko kugeza ku itariki ya 27 Gashyantare, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hakorewe ibizamini bitarenga 4000.
Ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, hatangiye gukorwa ibizamini bitarenga 14 000.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko: Abenshi mu barwayi, nubwo bari bafite ibimenyetso n'amabwiriza ya muganga, bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi yo kwitegura ibizamini Nyuma y'uko ku ya 29 Gashyantare muri leta ya Washington hatangajwe ko ariho habonetse umuntu wa mbere wapfuye azize coronavirus muri Amerika, guverineri Jay Insley yatangaje ko habaho ibihe bidasanzwe, ndetse n'ibindi bihugu na byo byatangaje ko bizaza.
Ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, amashuri yo mu mujyi wa Seattle yahagaritswe, kandi mu kwezi kwa gatatu hagati amashuri yari afunze mu gihugu hose. Ku itariki ya 6 Werurwe 2020, itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo bo muri kaminuza ya Imperial College, mu mujyi wa Londres, bamenyesheje Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika ku byerekeye ingaruka z'icyorezo cya coronavirus gishya ku gihugu.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ryo gutanga inkunga y'inyongera yo guhangana na coronavirus, ryemereraga leta z'igihugu gutanga inkunga y'ibiciro bya miliyari 8,3 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho imipaka ku ngendo z'abakozi, yahagaritse inama, kandi asaba abakozi gukora bari mu rugo.
Ibirori bya siporo n'ibihe by'imikino byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko atazongera kujya mu bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi, uretse mu Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yongeyeho n'u Bwongereza na Irilande.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, perezida yatangaje ibihe bidasanzwe mu gihugu, bituma hashyirwaho uburyo bwo gukoresha amafaranga ya leta mu guhangana n'ikibazo.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibigo byinshi byatangiye gufunga cyangwa kugabanya amasaha y'akazi muri Amerika yose, mu rwego rwo gufasha kurwanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyemejwe muri leta 50 zose no mu Ntara ya Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko i New York hagezweho abantu 10,700 banduye mu munsi umwe, barenga umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko gutandukanya abantu bishobora kuba ari ingamba nziza, kuko imibare y'abandura yagabanutse kuva ku munsi wa 2 kugeza ku munsi wa 4.7.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, i New York hari hamaze kuboneka abantu 32,308 banduye, naho 672 barapfuye. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hemejwe abantu benshi banduye coronavirus kurusha mu bindi bihugu byose byo ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Ku itariki ya 8 Mata, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hemejwe abantu 400,335 banduye, naho 12,841 barapfuye.
Nk'uko itangazamakuru ryabitangaje ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe, Perezida Trump yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera igihe cyo kwirinda abantu kugeza ku itariki ya 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwa USNS Comfort bufite ibitanda 1000 bwashyize ikirindiro mu cyambu cya New York.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, abantu 884 bishwe na coronavirus mu masaha 24.
Mu mujyi wa New York, umubare w'abanduye warenze 100,000 ku ya 3 Mata. Inzu y'Umurenge yahawe igitutu kubera ko itita ku byago no kugenzura amakuru agera ku bantu bose, ikoresheje ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence mu kugenzura imvugo n'ibitabo by'abategetsi n'abahanga mu by'ubuzima bijyanye na virusi.
Muri rusange, ibitekerezo by'abashyigikiye Perezida Trump ku kuntu ashoboye guhangana n'ikibazo byatandukanye.
Bamwe mu bayobozi n'abarezi banenze ko Amerika ikenera ibicuruzwa by'ingenzi, harimo n'ibikenewe, bivuye mu Bushinwa.
Mu kwezi kwa mbere mu mwaka wa 2020, ikinyamakuru Travel Medicine cyasohoye isesengura ry'ingendo zo mu kirere, ryakoreshejwe mu gupima no guhanura uburyo indwara zikwirakwira.
Ishyirahamwe Mpuzamahanga ry'Inyambukira ryavuze ko mu mwaka wa 2018, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ari byo byakiriye abagenzi benshi cyane baturutse i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byafatwaga nk'ahantu hakunzwe cyane n'abo bashyitsi.
Mu bice 20 by'ingenzi by'ubukerarugendo, Bali ni yo yavuzwe ko ititeguye cyane guhangana n'icyorezo, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya ari yo yavuzwe ko yiteguye cyane.
Muri iyi nkuru, bivugwa ko hari byinshi bigomba kumenyekana kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izita cyane ku kugenzura imipaka no gutangaza amakuru mu gihe hari ibyago.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hashyizweho itegeko ry'umutekano w'ikiremwamuntu.
Kubera ingamba z'ubwirinzi zifite ingaruka nziza mu gutwara abantu mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byateguye guhungisha abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba dipolomasi muri ako karere, cyane cyane binyuze mu ngendo z'indege z'ibihugu byabo, ibyo bikaba byemejwe n'ubutegetsi bw'u Bushinwa.
Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Tayilande ni bamwe mu bantu ba mbere bateganyaga guhungisha abaturage babo.
Pakisitani yatangaje ko itazatumiza abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yakuye muri icyo gihugu abaturage 34 bo muri Burezili, hamwe n'Abanyapolonye bane, Umunyashinwa n'Umuhindi.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, u Bushinwa n'u Buhinde bahagurukiye muri Polonye, aho indege yo muri Brezili yahagaritse mbere yo kujya muri Brezili nk'uko byari biteganyijwe.
Abaturage ba Brazil bari basuye Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi y'umujyi wa Brasilia.
Kuri uwo munsi, abaturage 215 bo muri Kanada (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere na 39 bari mu ya kabiri, bakodeshejwe na leta ya Amerika) bakuwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, bajyanwa ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Canada cya Trenton, bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye abaturage 185 bo muri Kanada, na bo bari bavuye i Wuhan, yaguye ku kigo cya CFB Trenton.
Ku itariki ya 3 n'iya 4 Gashyantare, abategetsi ba Australia bakuye abaturage babo 277 mu kigo cy'abashyitsi kiri ku kirwa cya Christmas, cyahindutse ikigo cyo kubarinda, aho bagumye iminsi 14.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, indege yo guhungisha abantu yavuye muri Nouvelle-Zélande igera mu mujyi wa Auckland; abagenzi bayo (harimo bamwe baturutse muri Ositaraliya no mu karere ka Aziya na Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cyo mu nyanja i Vangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangaje ko zizakuraho abaturage ba Amerika bari mu bwato bw'ubwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abantu 129 b'Abanyakanada bari bavuye mu bwato bwitwaga Diamond Princess, yaguye i Trenton, mu ntara ya Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubuhinde yatangiye guhungisha abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yari yaraguzwe na leta ya Afurika y'Epfo yahagurutse irimo abaturage 112 bo muri Afurika y'Epfo.
Abagenzi bagenzuwe mbere yo kugenda, kandi abantu bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus basigaye mu Bushinwa kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago byo kwandura.
Abavuye muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ko nta cyorezo cya coronavirus bafite ni bo bonyine bahawe uburenganzira bwo kwimuka.
Ibipimo byafashwe ku baturage bose ba Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abakozi bo mu ndege, abapilote, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, kandi nk'uburyo bwo kwirinda bose bagumye bakurikiranwe kandi bashyizwe mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 muri The Ranch Resort.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangiye gukura ingabo zayo muri Iraki mu rugero bitewe n'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarusi, Pakisitani, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje imfashanyo mu Bushinwa.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri b'Abashinwa biga muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bafatanyije mu gukusanya no kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'Ubushinwa byazahajwe na virusi, aho itsinda ryo muri Chicago ryavuzwe ko ryohereje imfashanyo ya N95 ibihumbi 50 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko batanze miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ya Amerika yo gushyigikira OMS mu gushyigikira ikorwa ry'urukingo no kuvura coronavirus, ndetse no kurinda abaturage b'ibihugu bya Afurika na Aziya y'Amajyepfo bafite ibyago byo kwandura iyi virusi.
Interaksyon yatangaje ko ku itariki ya 6 Gashyantare, leta y'Ubushinwa yahaye Filipines udupfukamunwa 200,000 nyuma y'uko Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje mu mujyi wa Wuhan udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16.
Ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare, umuryango wa Croix Rouge wa Singapore watangaje ko ugiye kohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani kandi bwatanze agapfukamunwa ka miliyoni imwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zisaga 13 z'imiti, Maleziya yatangaje ko yatanze imyenda y'imiti miliyoni 18, Ubudage bwohereje ibikoresho bitandukanye birimo udupfukamunwa ibihumbi 10, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatanze toni 17.8 z'imiti, kandi yiyemeza gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari nk'inkunga y'amafaranga ku bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo. Nyuma y'uko ibintu byatangiye kuba byiza mu Bushinwa, iki gihugu cyongeye kohereza imfashanyo mu bindi bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje imiti n'impuguke mu Butaliyani kugira ngo bifashe abaturage guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje umuryango w'ubumwe bwa Afurika, Addis Ababa, Ethiopia, imigabane ya miliyoni 1.1 yo gupima, miliyoni 6 z'udupfukamunwa n'imyambaro 60,000 yo kurinda umubiri kugira ngo ishyirahamwe rijye kubibwira ibihugu by'abanyamuryango.
Nyuma yaho, yohereje i Panama ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'ibikoresho 5 byo gupima amaraso.
Ma kandi yatanze imiti muri Canada. Ubuholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Czech byatangaje impungenge ku masike y'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yakuye mu Bushinwa ibikoresho 58 000 byo gupima coronavirus, bifite ubushobozi bwo gupima 30% gusa, naho Ubuholandi bukura mu Bushinwa udupfukamunwa 600 000 twahiye.
U Bubiligi kandi bwasubije inyuma udupfukamunwa 100,000 tutakibereye gukoreshwa: byatekerezwaga ko twakorewe mu Bushinwa, ariko nyuma byaje kugaragara ko twakomotse muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubufasha bw'u Bushinwa bwakiriwe neza mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangiye ibikorwa byo gufasha mu buryo bwihutirwa ibihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye cyane ingufu z'ubutegetsi bw'Ubushinwa mu kurwanya icyorezo no gukumira ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro rikomeye hagati y'icyorezo cya Pneumonia Atypical cyabaye mu mwaka wa 2002-2004, aho abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bashinjwaga ko bahishaga amakuru, ngo bigatuma indwara idashobora gukwirakwira, n'ikibazo cyo muri iki gihe, aho leta y'u Bushinwa yahaye amakuru mashya ku buryo abantu batagira ubwoba mu gihe cy'umwaka mushya w'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza icyemezo cy'ubutegetsi bw'ibanze cyo guhagarika ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, umuvugizi wa OMS, Goden Galea yavuze ko nubwo iki cyemezo cyari cyasabwe na OMS, ari igihamya gikomeye cyo kubahiriza inshingano zo gukumira icyorezo mu karere kiganjemo cyane, avuga ko ari ibitigeze bibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange. Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko ubwandu bushobora gukwirakwira ku bantu hanze y'Ubushinwa no kwiyongera kw'abanduye mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko ari ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mu rwego rw'ubuzima rusange gifite akamaro ku rwego mpuzamahanga (PICHE); iki cyari icya gatandatu kuva mu 2009 ubwo iki cyemezo cyakoreshwaga mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere cy'ibicurane by'inka.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Bwana Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko gutangaza PHEIC biterwa n'akaga ko gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amafaranga make n'agati mu gihugu, bidafite uburyo bwiza bwo kwivuza.
Mu kuvuga ku byemezo by'ingendo, Bwana Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gushyiraho ingamba zituma habaho inzitizi z'urudaca mu ngendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi" kandi ko "WHO idashishikariza abantu guhagarika ubucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu rwego rwo kwitegura icyorezo mu bihugu bikennye, ivuga ko ari ngombwa ko haboneka ubufasha bwihutirwa mu bihugu bifite uburyo bwo kumenya abantu banduye virusi, nubwo icyorezo kitaragera muri ibyo bihugu.
Bwana Tedros yavuze kandi ko "igaragaza uburyo twiteguye" ari uko twiteguye icyorezo cy'uruhande rwacu rw'intege nke cyane", asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "guhitamo: gushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura ejo". Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru cyabaye ku wa 11 Gashyantare, OMS yashyizeho izina ry'ubuvuzi  COVID-19.
Kuri uwo munsi Tedros yatangaje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, Antonio Guterres yemeye guha "ubushobozi bw'imikorere yose ya Loni mu gusubiza ikibazo".
Ibi byatumye hashyirwaho itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bibazo by'iki cyorezo, rigamije guhuza ibisubizo byose by'umuryango w'abibumbye, kandi OMS ivuga ko ibi bizatuma "ibisobanuro by'ubuvuzi byibanda ku kwihutisha ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi, mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora gukoresha ubumenyi bwazo mu guhangana n'icyorezo mu rwego rw'imibereho n'ubukungu".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, OMS n'u Bushinwa byatangije itsinda ryihariye ryashyizweho n'umuryango mpuzamahanga wita ku buzima, ryashyizeho impuguke mpuzamahanga n'abakozi ba OMS mu Bushinwa kugira ngo bafashe mu gukemura ikibazo cyo mu gihugu no gusuzuma uburemere bw'indwara n'ubwandu bwayo, bateguye amahugurwa n'inama n'inzego z'igihugu ziyoboye, ndetse no kujya mu duce kugira ngo basuzume ingaruka z'ingamba zo guhangana ku rwego rw'intara n'uturere, harimo n'imidugudu n'imidugudu. Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yavuze ko isi igomba gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora kwaduka, ivuga ko  hakiri kare kwita iki cyorezo icyorezo, ariko ibihugu bigomba kubitegura.
Igihe iki cyorezo cyatangiraga muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'abantu kugira ngo rigenzure uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko bishoboka ko coronavirus ikwirakwira ku isi hose izava kuri "yinshi" kugeza kuri "yinshi cyane" ku rwego rwo hejuru rw'ubwiteganyirize n'ibyago.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda ya WHO ishinzwe ibibazo by'ubuzima by'ibihe bidasanzwe, yatanze umuburo mu itangazo agira ati: Ni isuzuma rya buri leta ku isi ku byerekeye uko yiteguye guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ikibazo: igihe kirageze ngo hagire igikorwa.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira ijya mu gihugu cyawe, kandi ugomba kwitegura, kandi yashimangiye ko gusubiza neza bishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibihe bibi cyane".
Ryan yavuze kandi ko amakuru ariho ubu atari yo asobanura ko abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage batangaza ko icyorezo cyugarije isi, yongeraho ko gutangaza icyorezo bizaba bisobanura ko "mu by'ukuri twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi azaba afite ibyago byo kwandura iyi virusi".
Tariki 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS yavuze ko OMS ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ubwiyongere bukabije bw'iki cyorezo ndetse n'ubwiyongere bw'ubushomeri ku kibazo. OMS yanenzwe bikomeye kubera uburyo bufatwa nk'ubudahagije ku gitekerezo cy'icyorezo, harimo no gutangaza nyuma y'igihe ikibazo cy'ubutabazi mu buzima rusange no gushyira virusi muri icyorezo.
Mu gusubiza iki kibazo, Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Bwana Tedros Adanom, yashyikirijwe ibaruwa isaba ko yegura, isinywa n'abantu 733.000 kugeza ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu za ONU zigera kuri mirongo zashimangiye akamaro ko kubahiriza uburenganzira bwa buri muntu muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo gufatwaho ingamba zo kurokora ubuzima, kandi ko inshingano yo gutegura izo ngamba ari iya leta.
Itsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura umutungo cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagomba na gato kuba urwitwazo rwo gutandukanya abantu runaka.
Abahanga bagaragaje ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira bwo kurindwa ubuzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abantu bo mu matsinda mato, abageze mu za bukuru, abimukira, abatagira aho baba, abaturage baba mu mimerere mibi cyane, imfungwa, impunzi n'andi matsinda ataramenyekana akeneye inkunga ya leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ishinzwe ubutegetsi iri gusuzuma ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage ziterwa n'ikibazo cya COVID-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Ibihugu by'i Burayi, O.E.C. n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Burezi, O.E.D. ryashyizeho urubuga rugamije gutanga amakuru ajyanye n'igihe kandi arambuye ku bijyanye n'ingamba zo guhangana n'ibibazo by'ubukungu mu bihugu byo hirya no hino ku isi, ndetse no gusanga ibitekerezo n'inama.
Uru rubuga rwa Digital rufite amakuru ajyanye n'ingamba z'ibihugu bitandukanye (Country Policy Tracker) zo gukomeza imibereho myiza y'abaturage n'ubukungu bw'isi, gukuraho ingaruka z'igihombo n'ingamba zo gutembera mu rwego rwo gufasha ibihugu kwigira ku bindi no guteza imbere uburyo bw'isi yose bwo guhangana na coronavirus.
Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yanenzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Minisitiri w'Abaminisitiri w'u Bwongereza Michael Gow na Eduardo Bolsonaro, umuhungu wa Perezida wa Burezili Jair Bolsonaro, kubera ibikorwa byayo byo kurwanya icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei yo mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi b'Inteko Ishinga Amategeko y'Ubushinwa (CPC) bo mu ntara bakuru birukanywe kubera ingamba zo gukumira icyorezo mu gice cyo hagati cy'Ubushinwa, kandi ibyo birukanywe bigaragaza ko batishimiye uko inzego za politiki z'icyo gihugu zagiye zisubiza icyo cyorezo muri utwo turere.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuga ko icyo cyemezo cyari kigamije kurinda Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa, Xi Jinping, uburakari bw'abaturage ku cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Abashinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijiang, ntibemeranya n'ibyavuzwe mbere ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan, ariko bashyigikiye igitekerezo cy'ubugambanyi cy'uko COVID-19 yakomotse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubuyobozi bwa Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Donald Trump bwise coronavirus "virusi y'Abashinwa" cyangwa "virusi ya Wuhan", buvuga ko "kugenzura mu Bushinwa byongerera ikibazo virusi ubu imaze kuba icyorezo ku isi" kandi ibyo byanenzwe n'abatanga ibitekerezo bamwe bavuga ko ubwo buryo ari ubusambanyi kandi ko "butuma ubuyobozi bwa perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika budashobora gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara".
The Daily Beast yabonye telegaramu ya leta ya Amerika irimo ubuhanga mu itumanaho, bigaragara ko bwakozwe n'akanama k'umutekano w'igihugu, harimo amagambo avuga kuri ubwo buryo: Byose biri mu Bushinwa.
Dusaba ko twakwirakwiza aya makuru mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo ikiganiro n'abanyamakuru ndetse no gutangaza ibiganiro kuri televiziyo. Amashyirahamwe nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg, yavuze ko ingufu z'Ubushinwa zo gufasha ibihugu byazahajwe na virusi, ari kimwe mu "byamamaza" bigamije kugira ingaruka ku isi.
Umuyobozi w'urwego rushinzwe politiki y'amahanga rw'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, Joseph Borrell, yaburiye ko hari "ingingo ya politiki y'ubutaka, irimo guharanira kugira uruhare binyuze mu itangazamakuru rya rubanda n'ibyo bita politiki y'ubuntu".
Borrell yavuze kandi ko Ubushinwa bukomeje guteza imbere igitekerezo cy'uruhare rwabwo nk'umufatanyabikorwa ufite inshingano kandi wizewe, bitandukanye na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Ubushinwa kandi bwasabye Amerika gukuraho ibihano kuri Syria, Venezuela na Iran, ndetse hari amakuru avuga ko bwohereje imfashanyo muri ibi bihugu bibiri bya nyuma.
Jack Ma yatanze udupfukamunwa 100.000 muri Cuba, twabujijwe kubera ibihano bya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika byashyizweho ku itariki ya 3 Mata.
Ubutegetsi bwa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika kandi bwashinjwe ko bwahinduye ingufu z'ubufasha bwagenewe ibindi bihugu, bukazishyira mu gihugu cyabwo.
Ibibazo by'ibanga byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi byavutse kandi hagati y'ibindi bihugu nka Ubudage, Otirishiya n'Ubusuwisi, Repubulika ya Tchèque n'Ubutaliyani.
Uretse ibyo, Turukiya yafashe ibikoresho bya RAV amagana byari bigenewe Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yanenze ko Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi udashyigikiye u Butaliyani bugarijwe na coronavirus.
Maurice Massari, Ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani muri EU, yavuze ko Ubushinwa ari bwo bwonyine bwitabiriye mu buryo bw'impande zombi.
Ibyo nta bwo bigaragaza neza ko hari ubumwe bw'u Burayi.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma y'ikiganiro cya telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani, Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya, Vladimir Putin, yateguye kohereza mu Butaliyani abasirikare b'Uburusiya, imodoka zihariye zo gukiza indwara n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyasubiyemo amagambo yavuzwe n'umuntu utazwi cyane mu rwego rwa politiki, avuga ko 80% by'imfashanyo yatanzwe n'u Burusiya ari imfabusa cyangwa nta nyungu nyinshi z'u Butaliyani.
Uwo muyobozi yashinje u Burusiya ko bushaka gushimisha isi yose mu rwego rwa "gipolitiki na dipolomasi".
Perezida wa Lombardy Attilio Fontana na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'Ubutaliyani Luigi Di Maio banze ibitero by'itangazamakuru kandi bashimira ubufasha bahawe.
U Burusiya kandi bwohereje indege y'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko mu "gutanga ubufasha kuri bagenzi be b'Abanyamerika, [Putin] atekereza ko igihe abacuruzi b'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga bo muri Amerika bazongera umuvuduko w'igikorwa, na bo bazaba bashobora gutanga ubufasha mu gihe bibaye ngombwa".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO Uwurinda-2020 iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye n'ibihugu bya Baltique  imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO nini cyane kuva intambara y'ubutita irangiye  izakorwa mu buryo buciriritse.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament Kate Hudson yanenze imyitozo ya Defender 2020 (Umurinzi-2020): Mu bihe by'ibibazo by'ubuzima rusange, gukora iyi myitozo ntibyabangamiye ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi bigize uyu mushinga gusa, ahubwo binashyira mu kaga ubuzima bw'abaturage bo mu bihugu bigomba gukora iyo myitozo.
Ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020, Perezida wa Irani, Hassan Rouhani, mu ibaruwa yasomwe yasabye abayobozi b'isi ubufasha, avuga ko igihugu cye kigorwa no kurwanya icyorezo kubera kubura uburyo bwo kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga kubera ibihano Amerika yafatiye Irani. Iki cyorezo cyateye Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gusaba ko yakurikiza politiki z'imibereho myiza ziganje mu bindi bihugu bikize, harimo gushyiraho sisitemu imwe y'ubuzima n'uburezi bw'abana, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango gitangwa n'amafaranga, no kongera inkunga y'ubuzima rusange.
Abahanga mu bya politiki bari biteze ko ibyo bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku mahirwe ya Donald Trump yo kongera gutorwa mu matora ya perezida ya 2020 kubera ko icyorezo cyatumye umubano w'ububanyi n'amahanga hagati y'u Buyapani na Koreya y'Epfo ugenda urushaho kuzamba.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "ingamba z'ubwirinzi" z'Ubuyapani nyuma y'uko u Buyapani butangaje ko umuturage wese uvuye muri Koreya y'Epfo azashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri mu duce twashyizweho na leta.
Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo watangiye gutandukana bitewe n'uko Perezida Moon Jae-in yabyitwayemo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zishimagiza ibyo perezida yakoze cyangwa basaba ko Bwana Muno yafungwa kubera uburyo leta itari ifite bwo guhangana n'icyorezo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuga ko icyo cyemezo cyatuma leta zikomeza ububasha bwazo.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yemeye guha Minisitiri w'Intebe Viktor Orban uburenganzira bwo kuyobora mu gihe kitarambiranye akoresheje amategeko, guhagarika imirimo y'inteko ishinga amategeko, gutegura amatora no guhana abantu bashinjwa gukwirakwiza amakuru y'ibinyoma kuri virusi n'ingamba za leta zo guhangana n'ikibazo.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyiswe impamvu y'ibibazo byinshi by'ibura ry'ibikoresho mu kurwanya icyorezo, kugura ibicuruzwa mu gihe cy'ubwoba no guhagarika ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikorwaremezo.
Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura indyo y'ibiribwa n'imiti cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika cyatanze umuburo ku kibazo cy'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, bitewe n'uko ababikeneye biyongereye ndetse n'ababibahaga bakabura ibyo babaha.
Mu midugudu imwe n'imwe, habaye n'ubucuruzi bw'ubwoba, bituma ibintu by'ibanze biboneka mu maduka, urugero nk'ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku n'amazi yafashe mu mazi, biva ku isoko, bituma habaho ibura ry'ibikoresho.
By'umwihariko, inganda z'ikoranabuhanga zirakangurira abantu ku byerekeye gutinda mu byo gutumiza ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Bwana Tedros Adanom, yavuze ko icyifuzo cyo gukoresha ibikoresho byo kwirinda cyikubye inshuro 100.
Ibyo byatumye ibiciro byiyongeraho inshuro 20 ugereranyije n'ibisanzwe, kandi bituma ibyangombwa by'ubuvuzi bitinda gutangwa mu gihe cy'amezi ane cyangwa atandatu.
Yatumye kandi ku isi hose habaho ikibazo cy'ubwirinzi bw'umuntu ku giti cye, kandi OMS yaburiye ko abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima bazaba bahanganye n'ikibazo cy'uburwayi.
Muri Ositaraliya, kubera icyorezo, abaguzi bakoresheje daigow bahawe uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Ibi byatumye ibiribwa by'abana bigabanuka mu masuporari amwe n'amwe, nyuma byahagaritswe na guverinoma ya Ositaraliya. Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, ndetse n'ibyifuzo byinshi by'ibiribwa, byirinze ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibiribwa mu turere twombi.
Ingamba zashyizweho n'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ibikorwa byo gukusanya ibicuruzwa n'ubucuruzi butemewe n'amategeko bw'ibikoresho by'ingenzi, zagize icyo zigeraho, zatumye hatabaho ubukene bukabije bw'ibiribwa bwari bwitezwe mu Burayi, ndetse no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
U Butaliyani bwo mu majyaruguru, aho umusaruro w'ubuhinzi ari muto, ntibwagize ibyago bikomeye byo kugabanuka, ariko abahagarariye uwo mugabane bavuga ko ibiciro by'ibikomoka ku buhinzi bishobora kuzamuka.
Amashami y'amaduka y'ibiribwa yagumye ahuze mu gihe gito, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu gihe abayobozi ba leta y'u Bushinwa bari bafite uburenganzira bwo kubona inyama z'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage bajye bahabwa ibyokurya bihagije.
Amategeko nk'ayo agenga abahinzi b'ibiribwa asaba ko babika ibiribwa mu gihe habaye ibintu bidasanzwe, na yo ariho mu Butaliyani.
Ibyangijwe mu bukungu bw'isi byibasiye u Bushinwa: nk'uko bitangazwa n'ibinyamakuru byo ku wa 16 Werurwe, ubukungu bw'u Bushinwa bwahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 kubera ingamba zafashwe na leta zo kurwanya ikwirakwira rya virusi, bituma igiciro cy'ibicuruzwa bya magurisha kigabanukaho 20,5%.
Ubushinwa ni igihugu gikomeye mu by'ubukungu n'inganda, bityo iki cyorezo cyitwa ko ari ikibazo gikomeye ku bukungu bw'isi.
Agate Demarai, umukozi muri Economist Intelligence Unit, avuga ko gucogora ku masoko bizakomeza kugeza igihe hazaba hari igitekerezo cyumvikana cy'ingaruka zishobora guturuka kuri ibyo bintu.
Muri Mutarama 2020, bamwe mu bashakashatsi bavuze ko ingaruka z'ubukungu bw'iki cyorezo ku bukungu bw'isi zishobora kurenga iz'icyorezo cya Pneumonia yo mu 2002-2004.
Hari igitabo cyavuze ko hari impungenge z'uko hari abantu benshi batagira icyo bakora kugira ngo babone ibyo bakeneye, kandi ko hari n'abandi benshi batagira icyo bakora kugira ngo babone ibyo bakeneye.
Bitangazwa ko Umuryango w'Ibihugu byohereza peteroli hanze (OPEC) watangiye gufata ingamba z'igihe gito nyuma y'uko ibiciro bya peteroli byagabanutse cyane kubera ko Ubushinwa bwagabanutse mu byo busaba.
Ku itariki ya 24 Gashyantare, amasoko y'imari ku isi yose yarasenyutse kubera umubare munini w'abantu banduye COVID-19 hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge zikomeje kwiyongera ku cyorezo cya coronavirus, ibipimo bitandukanye by'imari bya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika birimo NASDAQ-100, S&P 500 na Dow Jones Index by'imigabane y'ibigo by'inganda, byagaragaje igwa rikomeye cyane kuva mu 2008, aho Dow Index yagabanutseho 1191  igwa rikomeye ry'umunsi umwe kuva mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'imari rya 2007-2008 .
Mu mpera z'icyumweru, ibipimo byose uko ari bitatu by'imigabane byaragabanutseho hejuru ya 10%.
Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, ikigo cy'ubucuruzi cya Scope Ratings GmbH cyemeje ko Ubushinwa bufite igipimo cy'inguzanyo cy'ubwigenge, ariko gikomeza kuvuga ko nta cyo buzaba.
Imigwi yongeye kugwa kubera impungenge z'ikwirakwira rya coronavirus, aho yagabanutse cyane ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko hari icyizere cy'uko ubukungu buzagabanuka.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu witwa Mohamed El-Erian yashimye cyane ingamba z'ubutabazi zafashwe n'amabanki nkuru y'igihugu n'ibihugu.
Banki nkuru z'igihugu zagize icyo zikora vuba kurusha uko byagenze mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'ubukungu ryo mu mwaka wa 2008.
Ubukerarugendo  ni kimwe mu bice byazahajwe cyane n'amategeko abuza abantu kujya mu mahanga, gufunga ahantu hahurira abantu benshi harimo n'ahantu hakunze guturwa n'abashoramari, ndetse no kuba leta zasabye abantu kutagira ingendo.
Kubera izo ngamba zose, kompanyi nyinshi z'indege zataye ingendo kubera kugabanuka cyane kw'ibyifuzo by'amatike y'indege, harimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines na Qantas, kandi kompanyi y'indege yo mu Bwongereza Flybe yahagaritse kubaho.
Ingaruka mbi ku rugendo rw'ubwato bwa Cruise yari ikomeye cyane kurusha mbere hose.
Sitasiyo za gari ya moshi nyinshi n'ibibuga by'indege byafunzwe.
Iki cyorezo cyahuriranye na Chung-yun, igihe cy'ubukerarugendo cy'umwaka mushya w'Ubushinwa.
Leta z'ibihugu n'iz'uturere zahagaritse ibikorwa byinshi by'abantu benshi, harimo n'iminsi mikuru ya buri mwaka y'umwaka mushya; ibigo byigenga na byo byafunze amaduka yabyo n'ahantu hakunzwe guturwa nk'ahitwa i Hong Kong na Shanghai.
Imikino myinshi yo kwizihiza umwaka mushya yahagaritswe, kandi ahantu hatembereye abantu benshi barafungwa kugira ngo hatazagira abantu benshi bahurira hamwe; urugero ni mu mujyi wa Beijing, ahari umujyi wabuzanyijwe, n'amahuriro ya kera y'insengero yahagaritswe.
Mu ntara 24, mu mirenge n'utugari 31 byo mu Bushinwa, abategetsi bongereye iminsi y'ikiruhuko cy'umwaka mushya kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Gashyantare, basaba ko inganda nyinshi zitagomba gufungura kugeza kuri iyo tariki.
Ibyo bice by'igihugu byinjizaga 80% by'umusaruro mbumbe w'igihugu na 90% by'ibyoherezwa mu mahanga.
Ubuyobozi bwa Hong Kong bwongereye umubare w'abandura indwara ku rwego rwo hejuru ndetse bwatangaje ko habaye ikibazo cy'ubukungu, bufunga amashuri kugeza muri Werurwe no guhagarika kwizihiza umwaka mushya.
Abantu bageraga ku maduka acuruza ibintu by'akataraboneka mu Burayi no muri Amerika y'Epfo bagabanutseho 40%.
Ubucuruzi bwo muri Amerika ya Ruguru no mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati bwagabanyije ibicuruzwa ku kigero cya 50 na 60%.
Ibyo byatumye abantu benshi bajya mu maduka muri Werurwe, bagabanukaho 33 ku ijana ugereranyije n'uko byari bimeze muri Gashyantare.
Abakora ibigo by'ubucuruzi ku isi hose bashyizeho ingamba z'inyongera, nko kunoza isuku, gushyiraho ibikoresho byo kugenzura ubushyuhe bw'abaza, no guhagarika ibikorwa. Komisiyo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ishinzwe ubukungu muri Amerika y'Epfo igaragaza ko ubukene muri Amerika y'Epfo bwatewe n'icyorezo gishobora gutuma abantu barenga miliyoni 14.22 bakomeza kubaho mu bukene kurusha uko byari bimeze mu gihe nta cyorezo.
Muri Mutarama na Gashyantare 2020, mu gihe icyorezo cyari cyiganje i Wuhan, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni eshanu mu Bushinwa batakaje akazi.
Benshi mu bakozi b'abimukira 300 miliyoni bo mu Bushinwa bari mu ngo zabo mu ntara z'igihugu cyabo cyangwa bafungiwe mu ntara ya Hubei. Muri Werurwe 2020, Abanyamerika barenga miliyoni 10 batakaje akazi maze basaba leta ubufasha.
Nk'uko bitangazwa na Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora gutwara abantu miliyoni 47 akazi, kandi umubare w'abashomeri ushobora kugera kuri 32%. Ingamba zo kwitarura abandi zashyizweho mu Buhinde zizatuma miliyoni mirongo y'abakozi b'abimukira b'Abahinde batagira akazi, bahabwa umushahara buri munsi. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'Ikigo cya Angus Reid bwagaragaje ko 44% by'ingo z'Abanyakanada zahuye n'ubushomeri mu buryo runaka. Abakozi hafi 900,000 bo muri Esipanye na bo batakaje akazi kuva mu kwezi kwa Werurwe 2020 ubwo muri Esipanye hatangizwaga gahunda yo gushyirwa mu kato.
Mu gice cya kabiri cya Werurwe, abakozi bagera kuri miliyoni 4 b'Abafaransa basabye inguzanyo y'igihe gito yo kubura akazi, naho miliyoni imwe y'Abongereza basaba inguzanyo imwe y'imibereho myiza.
Gahunda y'ubudage yo guhemba abakozi bakora igihe gito na yo yashyizwe mu bikorwa mu Bufaransa no mu Bwongereza.
Ubuhanzi n'umurage w'umuco nabyo byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo cyibasiye ibikorwa by'imiryango ndetse n'abantu ku giti cyabo, baba abafite akazi cyangwa abikorera ku giti cyabo, hirya no hino ku isi.
Imiryango y'umuco n'ubuhanzi yagerageje gushyigikira ubutumwa bwayo (benshi buhererekanywa na leta) bwo gutanga umusaruro ku murage w'umuco ku baturage, byemeza umutekano w'abakozi bayo n'abaturage, kandi, aho bishoboka, bishyigikira abantu b'ubuhanzi.
Muri Werurwe 2020, amazu ndangamurage, amabaruwa, inzu z'ibitaramo n'ibindi bigo by'umuco byari byafunzwe ku isi hose kugeza igihe kitamenyekanye, cyangwa ku buryo butandukanye, kandi imurika, ibikorwa n'ibitaramo byahagaritswe cyangwa byimuriwe ku yindi minsi.
Mu gihe cya vuba aha, hari ibindi bikorwa by'ubucuruzi byagiye bikorwa, harimo no guhagarika ibikorwa by'idini, siporo n'ibindi bikorwa by'abaturage, nk'ibirori by'umuziki n'ibitaramo, inama z'ikoranabuhanga n'ibyerekanwa by'imideri.
Mu by'ukuri, Vatican yatangaje ko itazongera gukora icyumweru cya Pasika i Roma, gihuza icyumweru cya nyuma cy'Ikarema.
Amatorero menshi y'i Burayi asaba Abakristo bageze mu za bukuru kuguma mu rugo no kutitabira amateraniro yo ku cyumweru; mu nsengero zimwe na zimwe, amateraniro yo mu rusengero yatangiye gutambutswa kuri radiyo, kuri televiziyo cyangwa ku buryo bwa videwo, mu gihe abayobozi b'amadini amwe n'amwe batanga inama yo guteranira mu cyumba cyo hejuru.
Kiliziya Gatolika y'i Roma yafunze insengero zayo, insengero n'ahantu hazwi nka St. Peter's Square, aho abasigaye b'abakristo batakiboneka, nyuma y'aho andi matorero na yo yahagaritse ibikorwa by'idini, kandi agabanya uburyo bwo gusengera mu nsengero, mu nsengero, mu nsengero z'Abayahudi, mu nsengero no mu bigo by'Abihaye Imana.
Minisiteri y'Ubuzima ya Irani yatangaje ko amasengesho yo ku wa gatanu yasubitswe mu turere twari twugarijwe n'icyorezo cya coronavirus, kandi ko insengero zafunzwe nyuma; Arabiya Sawudite yabujije abimukira n'abaturage bayo kwinjira mu nsengero za Mecca na Medina.
Icyorezo cyateje impinduka zikomeye cyane mu mikino mpuzamahanga kuva mu Ntambara ya Kabiri y'Isi.
