Icyorezo cya COVID-19  ni ikintu cyerekanye isano abantu bafitanye n'abandi ku isi hose n'inshingano dufitanye.
Nta kibazo nk'iki twari dufite, ariko tuzi ko kugira ngo ibyo dukora bigire ingaruka nziza, bisaba ko twishyira mu mwanya w'abandi, tugakorana, kandi tugatera imbere mu muryango w'abantu ku isi hose, ari byo by'ibanze bituma twubaka umuryango.
Twabonye imishyikirano y'inshuti n'ubwuzu hagati y'abo dukorana bose, ibyo bikaba byaragaragaragaye mu ma-mail, amatelefone no mu biganiro bya buri munsi - ni igihamya cyiza cy'uko, ku bw'amahirwe, dufite abantu badasanzwe dukorana.
