Nibukijwe akamaro ko kuba Wikipedia ishobora kugera ku isi muri iki gihe, n'akamaro ko kugira uru rubuga rwa interineti rw'ibanze kuri buri muntu.
Ibyo byose bishoboka bitewe n'akazi mukora, haba mu gutuma urubuga rukora neza, mu kwishyura bagenzi bacu cyangwa mu kurinda umutekano w'abaturage.
Isi ikeneye amakuru ari muri Wikipedia, kandi ubu ni ngombwa kurusha mbere hose.
Muri ibi bihe, kugira ngo tugere ku bintu by'ingenzi ku isi, ntabwo ari ibyo dukora gusa, ahubwo ni uburyo tubikora.
Kubera akamaro k'iki gikorwa n'uruhare rwawe muri icyo gikorwa, tugiye kugira impinduka zikomeye mu mikorere y'akazi kacu, guhera mu cyumweru gitaha.
Gukosora gahunda y'akazi kacu n'amasaha tugenderaho
Nk'uko Robin yabitangaje mbere, itsinda rya C-team ryateranye mu ijoro ryakeye kugira ngo rigire icyo rivuga ku buryo tuzakoresha igihe cyacu n'igihe tuzakoresha mu minsi n'amezi ari imbere.
Mu kiganiro twagiranye, twaganiriye ku bitekerezo byacu ku ngamba z'ingirakamaro mu bihe biriho n'uburyo bwiza bwo gutuma umuryango ukomera muri ibi bihe.
Abenshi muri twe twifuzaga kureka ibintu bikaza nyuma, kugira ngo dukomeze umurimo wacu w'igihe kirekire.
