Ku bakozi bose, abakora mu mishinga n'abakozi ba bwite:
Twateganyaga ko tuzakora amasaha agera kuri 4 ku munsi cyangwa amasaha 20 mu cyumweru kugeza igihe tuzabona andi mabwiriza.
Ntabwo dutangaza iminsi y'ikiruhuko: niba ushobora gukora amasaha menshi mu buryo busanzwe, biremewe kubw'intego z'umwuga wacu.
Ariko isi muri iki gihe ntishobora kwitegereza; ibyo waba ukeneye byose, byaba kwita ku muryango wawe, kugura ibiribwa cyangwa kujya kwa muganga, imibereho yawe myiza  ni yo ifite agaciro ka mbere.
Ntitugenzura amasaha mukora.
Niba urwaye, ntugomba gukora.
Ibyo birumvikana kandi nta gushidikanya, ariko turabivuga.
Nta ruhushya rw'ibitaro cyangwa ikiruhuko cy'ikiruhuko ukeneye: gusa bimenyeshe umuyobozi wawe, kandi ufashe itsinda gusubiramo kalendari n'ingengabihe y'akazi kugira ngo urebe ko ibintu by'ingenzi bikubiyemo.
(Niba wemejwe ko ufite COVID-19, bwira Brian muri T&C Ops kugira ngo T&C ishobore gutanga inkunga n'ibisobanuro by'ubuyobozi ku kibazo cyawe).
Amafaranga y'isaha yose azishyurwa mu buryo bwuzuye.
Twatangaje kandi turemeza ko tuzakurikiza amasezerano yacu ku bakoresha bacu n'abakozi bacu ku isaha.
Buri muntu wese azahabwa umushahara ku isaha nk'uko bisanzwe bikorwa mu mimerere isanzwe.
Ibyo by'umwihariko bikubiyemo igihe cy'uburwayi utashobora gukora.
Niba ushaka gukora, turagushyigikiye.
Abantu benshi bakoresha akazi nk'uburyo bwo gushyira imbaraga zabo mu isi idukikije.
Ibyo dukora bishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye cyane cyane mu bihe nk'ibi.
Kandi nanone, ni ukwishyira mu mwanya wa mbere.
Turagusaba kuvugana n'umuyobozi wawe kugira ngo tumenye icyo twakwitega, bityo dushobore guhindura imikorere yacu mu buryo bukwiriye.
Hari imirimo imwe n'imwe iba ari iy'ingenzi.
Ibyo ni ibintu tugomba guhora dushyigikira.
Amatsinda ya SRE, HR Ops, Trust&Safety na Fundraising (mu bandi) akora akazi gakomeye gashobora gukenera ubufasha bw'inyongera.
Turimo gutangiza inzira ku nzego zose zo gusuzuma intego z'iki gihe no guhindura icyerekezo cyo gutanga inkunga, ari nacyo kintu cy'ingenzi ku butumwa bwacu.
Hariho byinshi byo gukora kuri buri wese muri twe, kandi twibanda gusa ku mishinga ifite agaciro cyane.
Guta igihe muri iki gihe ntibisobanura ko hari ingaruka mbi zizagira mu gihe kizaza.
Ntitugiteganya gukora inshuro ebyiri kugira ngo dushobore kugera ku byo twabuze nyuma y'icyorezo.
Si ngombwa ko ukora amasaha y'ikirenga kugira ngo uhuze n'igihe ntarengwa cyo muri iki gihe.
