Kugira ngo duhindure imikorere n'ibyo abantu bategereje ku gihe cy'akazi ka buri munsi, tugiye guhindura igihe cyo gushyira mu bikorwa gahunda y'umwaka wa 2020-2021.
Turateganya gutanga ingengabihe y'igishushanyo mbonera cyacu cya 2019-2020, bityo tukagira igihe kinini cyo gushyiraho ingengo y'imari, bityo tukemurira abakozi gushyira imbere imirimo ikomeye, kwifasha no kwita ku bo bakunda, kandi mu gihe abantu bose bakeneye cyangwa bashaka gukora bahabwa igihe gito mu byumweru bike biri imbere.
Iyo mirimo y'igihe kirekire ituma umuteguro wose ugabanya cyane akazi n'imihangayiko.
Mu cyumweru gitaha tuzatanga igitekerezo cyacu ku nama, tuzatanga amakuru ajyanye n'ingamba zikurikira ku bayobozi n'amatsinda ako kanya tubonye icyemezo gifatika.
Turashimira itsinda rya APP ku ruhare rwabo mu kuyobora iki gikorwa.
Imimerere y'ibiro, ibyago n'isuku
Mu cyumweru gishize, twamenye ko umwe mu bo dukorana i San Francisco ashobora kuba yaranduye COVID-19.
Icyakora, uretse kwirinda ibintu byinshi, twashyizeho itsinda ryo gusukura virusi kugira ngo rihumane ibintu byose byo ku biro byacu biri i San Francisco.
Bakoresheje umuti wo kurwanya virusi mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi mu gusukura imiterere yose, ndetse no mu byumba by'abashyitsi n'ibyumba by'amazu y'abazamuka, aho bashoboraga kwinjira mu igorofa ryacu.
Inzu ikurikiza amategeko yayo, agaragaza ko umuntu agomba kwitonda, akoresha ibikoresho bifasha abahatuye.
Twumva ko ibiro byacu bizaba byiteguye neza igihe tuzaba tugiye kugaruka.
Ibiro byacu byo mu Ntara ya Columbia biri mu muyoboro wa WeWork, watugejejeho n'abakozi bose bari muri DC amabwiriza ajyanye na COVID-19.
Mu cyumweru gishize, ibiro byacu byo mu karere ka Columbia byatangiye gukora imirimo yo mu rwego rwo hanze hakurikijwe amabwiriza yatanzwe na San Francisco.
Nk'uko bamwe mu bo dukorana muri New York babizi, twaganiriye no ku birebana no gukodesha inzu i Brooklyn.
Ibi biganiro bikomeje, ariko bishobora gusubikwa.
Bamwe mu bo dukorana ni ubwa mbere bakorera kure.
Abagenzi bacu ba kera bakorera kure bazi ko bishoboka gukosora ibintu kandi bifuza kubaha inama:
Ni byiza ko amateraniro aba ari amasaha abiri cyangwa arenze.
Niba ukeneye amasomo arenze ayo, tekereza ku kuyasubiramo mu byiciro by'iminsi myinshi.
Sobanura neza intego y'inama, gahunda yayo kandi utange inyandiko z'ibanze mbere y'igihe.
Koresha videwo by'ibanze, kandi ukoreshe ibikoresho nka Google Docs na Zoom kugirango byorohereze imikoranire no gutumanaho.
Kugira ngo bigire isuku, shyiraho umuhuzabikorwa  umuntu uzakurikirana ibibazo mu kiganiro no kugenzura urutonde rw'abavuga, kandi ushyireho n'umuntu ushinzwe kwandika (cyangwa gusangira).
Niba ukeneye gukoresha imashini ikora neza, ushobora kujya kuri interineti kuri serivisi z'ubufasha.
Koresha inyungu zo muri gahunda ya Wellness Reimbursement mu gihe ugura amafunguro y'ibyokurya byoroheje.
Fata urubuga rwa #remoties kuri Slack kugira ngo uganire na bagenzi bawe ku bijyanye n'akazi gahabwa abantu.
Itsinda rya HR Operations ririmo kwiga amabwiriza ajyanye na ergonomie aboneka mu buryo bwa webinar kugira ngo atume akazi gatangwa mu rwego rw'umuryango kose kagenda neza.
Mu cyumweru gishize, twasabye abantu bose bahawe inkunga n'umuryango guhagarika ibikorwa by'abantu benshi bishyigikiwe na Wikimedia, nka editathons, kugeza igihe OMS itangarije ko icyorezo kirangiye.
Turasobanukiwe kandi turamenyesha ko gusaba kwacu ko ibyo byemezo bivanwaho cyangwa ibindi bibangamira bishobora gutuma ibikorwa by'inguzanyo byemeranyijwe bitashoboka, kandi nta muntu uzatozwa igihano kubera gutinda guhatirwa cyangwa guhindura intego.
Mu cyumweru gitaha tuzakomeza ibikorwa by'ubufatanye, tuzabagezaho andi mabwiriza ajyanye na Wikimania ndetse n'andi makoraniro y'akarere n'ay'umuryango.
Umwuka rusange mu muryango mpuzamahanga  ntabwo ari agahinda gusa kubera guhagarika akazi, ahubwo ni n'ibyishimo biterwa no gusobanukirwa no kwibanda ku muryango wacu, Wikimedia ndetse n'ahandi.
Ku bijyanye n'ibisobanuro, CRT iri gukora ku rubuga rwa Meta-Wiki ruzatanga umwanya w'umuryango wo gukurikirana ingaruka n'itumanaho.
Dukomeje kuvugana ku bibazo bijyanye na COVID-19
Tuzabashyira ku rutonde rw'amateraniro adasanzwe y'abakozi azaba ku wa Kane, saa kumi n'ebyiri UTC/07:00 PT.
Kuri iyi nshuro tuzaba dufashe umwanya wo gusangira amakuru agezweho, gusubiza ibibazo byanyu no kumarana igihe hamwe, duhuza.
Turi kumwe muri ibi bihe, kandi twiteguye gufasha mu buryo bwose dushoboye.
Ariko ushobora gukomeza kubona amakuru yo kuri iyi e-mail, n'andi makuru y'ingenzi kuri COVID-19  muri Office Wiki.
CRT izajya ihindura ayo mapaji, kandi amakuru yose azaba ari ahantu hamwe.
Turimo kandi dukora ibishoboka byose kugira ngo dukomeze gushyikirana n'abakozi bacu baba mu bihugu byazahajwe cyane n'iki kibazo.
Niba ufite ibibazo ku bijyanye n'ingendo, ibikorwa, gahunda y'akazi, ibibazo byo gutanga amakuru cyangwa se niba ukeneye ubufasha bw'ubundi buryo, shaka CRT.
Turiho kugira ngo tubashyigikire kandi dufashe mu gihe bibaye ngombwa.
Niba ufite ikibazo cy'ibanga, andikira Brian Judan  Umuyobozi wa HR International Global Operations.
Nta mpinduka nk'izo zagombye gufatwa nk'aho ari ukuva mu kazi kacu no mu nshingano zacu.
Ahubwo ni ukwemera ko hari igihe dushobora gukenera guhindura imikorere yacu n'ibyo dukora.
Twizera ko izi ntambwe ari ngombwa kugira ngo dushigikirane kandi dushobore gukomeza gukora, kugira ngo dushobore gutanga inkunga ikenewe ku rugendo rwacu no ku isi yose dukoresheje serivisi ikenewe.
Ibikorwa byacu byateganyijwe bizategereza igihe gikwiriye.
Uyu munsi ni igihe cyo gufashanya no kurema umwanya w'akazi k'ingenzi mu byumweru biri imbere ndetse wenda no mu mezi ari imbere.
Kugira ngo ibyo bibe, dukeneye ubufasha bw'umuntu wese muri mwe; kandi dukeneye ko mushobora kwitunga no kwita ku miryango yanyu, kandi mukora uko mushoboye kose igihe bibaye ngombwa.
