Enzyme ihindura angiotensin 2 (ACE2) ni enzyme ifata ku bice by'inyuma (membrane z'ingirabuzimafatizo) z'ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu maraso.
ACE2 irwanya ibikorwa bya angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) ikora, igabanya igipimo cya angiotensin-II no kongera Ang (1-7), bigatuma iba umuti wizewe mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. AC2 kandi ikora nk'aho yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi zimwe.
Impamvu abantu bakoresha iyi enzyme ni uko ari yo yitwa hACE2.
Enzyme ihindura angiotensin 2  ni metaloferment irimo zinc, iri ku butaka bw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso n'izindi.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 irimo N-extrinsic peptidaze domain ya M2 na C-extrinsic transport domain ya collectrin ya amino acide ya renal.
ACE2 ni poroteyine yo mu bwoko bwa I, ifite ubushobozi bwo gukora mu buryo bw'ibinyabutabire, kandi ifata uruzitiro rw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibihaha n'izindi.
Urubuga rwo hanze y'ingirabuzimafatizo ya ACE2 ruvanwa ku rundi rwa transmembrane na ferum imwe izwi nka sheddaze, maze poroteyine iboneka ikajya mu maraso, amaherezo ikajya mu cyondo.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifatanye na membrane y'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ingirabuzimafatizo nyinshi z'ubuhumekero z'ubwoko bwa II, intanga nke z'amaraso, intanga z'amaraso n'iz'amaraso, intanga z'amaraso z'amaraso n'iz'imitsi y'amaraso y'ingingo nyinshi.
Biosynthesis ya ACE2 na RNA iboneka no mu gice cy'ubwonko, muri striatum, mu gice cy'ubuhumekero no mu gice cy'ubwonko.
Umurimo w'ibanze wa ACE2 ni ugukora nk'urwanya ACE.
ACE isenya ingirabuzimafatizo yitwa angiotensin I ikavamo angiotensin II.
ACE2 nayo ifata karuboksile ya amino acide ya phenylalanine ikava muri angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikajya mu cyiciro cya angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
