Uburyo bworoshye bwo kubigeraho, ni ugukoresha Bluetooth kugira ngo umuntu ashobore kumenya aho ari kuri telefoni ye.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple batangaje ko bagiye guhuza imbaraga zabo mu guhuza imikorere yo gushyigikira porogaramu nk'izi zishingiye kuri Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu zikoranabuhanga za Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta yafatanyije na Alipay gutangiza porogaramu ituma abaturage bashobora kureba niba bakoranaga n'abantu banduye COVID-19.
Ikoreshwa mu mijyi 200 yo mu Bushinwa.
Porogaramu yakozwe n'ibigo byaho by'ikoranabuhanga, ifite kode ifunguye kandi izashyikirizwa leta. Macedonia y'Amajyaruguru yatangije porogaramu ya StopKorona! ikora kuri Bluetooth, ifasha gukurikirana abantu bashobora kuba banduye kandi ikanafasha mu guhana amakuru n'inzego z'ubuzima.
Iyi porogaramu yakozwe n'ubumwe bwa Minisiteri y'Itumanaho n'Ikoranabuhanga n'ubw'Umurimo w'Ubuzima.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Mata 2020, iyi porogaramu yari itegereje kwiyandikisha muri Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abantu iri mu cyiciro cya nyuma cy'iterambere kandi ko izatangira gukoreshwa mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'izo ziteganyijwe gutangira muri Ireland no mu Bufaransa (StopCovid).
Australia na Nouvelle Zelande birimo kureba uburyo bwo gukoresha porogaramu zishingiye kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether yo muri Singapuru na BlueTrace. Uburusiya bufite intego yo gukoresha porogaramu ifite uburyo bwo kugenzura aho abantu bavurwa COVID-19 batuye i Moscou baturuka.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu muri kaminuza ya Cambridge wigisha iby'umutekano, avuga ibibazo byinshi bishobora kuvuka mu mikorere y'ibikoresho, harimo no gukora ibintu bitari byo no kutagira umusaruro mu gihe porogaramu ikoreshwa n'abantu bake.
Kubera impungenge z'ikwirakwira ry'imikoreshereze ya "coronavirus" ibeshya cyangwa yangiza, Apple yagabanyije urutonde rw'imiryango ishobora gutanga imikoreshereze yayo ifitanye isano na "coronavirus" kuri App Store, ikishyira gusa "ibanze" cyangwa indi miryango yizewe.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abari muri iyo gahunda yo kurinda ubuzima bwite bw'abantu bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka zo kugenzura abaturage mu buryo bwagutse hakoreshejwe porogaramu z'ikoranabuhanga zifitanye isano na coronavirus; by'umwihariko, havuzwe niba ibikorwa remezo byo kugenzura byashyizweho mu rwego rwo kurwanya icyorezo cya coronavirus bizasenywa igihe iterabwoba rizaba ritakiriho.
Umuryango "Amnesty International" n'andi mashyirahamwe asaga 100 yasohoye itangazo risaba ko ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura bukorwa mu buryo buciriritse.
Amashyirahamwe yatangaje ibintu umunani asaba ko bikorwa ku mishinga ya Leta:
kugenzura bigomba kuba byemewe n'amategeko, bikenewe kandi bihuje n'imimerere;
kwagura kugenzura no kugenzura bigomba kujyana n 'impamvu z 'uko igihe cy 'ibikorwa cyabyo cyagombye kugabanywa;
Gukoresha amakuru bigomba guhagarikwa hagamijwe kurwanya ikwirakwira rya COVID-19;
umutekano n'ubwirinzi by'ibanga bigomba kurindwa, kandi hagomba gutangwa ibimenyetso by'uko byarinzwe;
kugenzura mu mibare bigomba kwirinda ibibazo by ' ivangura no gukumira abandi;
guhanahana amakuru kose n 'abashyingiranywe bigomba kuba byarateganyijwe ku rwego rw 'amategeko;
