Mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe, aho gukoresha porogaramu, hakoreshwa uburyo bwo gukurikirana aho umuntu ari kuri interineti, ibyo bikaba bituma umuntu atagomba gukuramo porogaramu cyangwa ngo agire ubushobozi bwo kwirinda gukurikiranwa.
Muri Isirayeli, hashyizweho amategeko agenga uburyo bwo gukurikirana abantu mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga.
