Ibimenyetso by'ibi byago birimo guhumeka nabi, kubabara cyane cyangwa kumva ufunze mu gatuza, guhungabana, kugira ingorane zo kubyuka, ubururu mu maso cyangwa mu kanwa; niba ibi bimenyetso byavuzwe haruguru biriho, ugomba gushaka ubufasha bw'abaganga.
