Iyi mibare itandukanye bitewe n'akarere. Bimwe mu bisubizo by'ubu buryo harimo kumenya umubare w'abapfa bazize indwara (CFR), ugaragaza umubare w'abarwayi bapfuye bazize indwara, hamwe no kumenya umubare w'abapfa bazize indwara (IFR), ugaragaza umubare w'abarwayi banduye (abapfuye bazize indwara n'abapfuye batazize indwara) bapfuye bazize indwara.
Izi mibare ntizifite igihe gifatika kandi zigaragaza imibare y'abantu batandukanye uhereye igihe batangiye kwandura kugeza igihe indwara irangiriye.
Nubwo abantu bose batandura batagira uduhimba tw'umubiri, iyo hari uduhimba tw'umubiri, dushobora kumenya umubare w'abantu banduye.
Mu mujyi wa Castiglione d'Adda mu Butaliyani, umudugudu muto utuwe n'abantu 4.600, abantu 80 (1,7%) barapfuye.
Mu mujyi wa Gangelt, indwara yageze ku rubyiruko mu gihe cy'iminsi mikuru y'iminsi mikuru, bituma umubare w'abapfa ugabanuka, kandi si abantu bose bapfuye bazira COVID-19 bashoboraga kubarirwa nk'abapfuye.
Byongeye kandi, sisitemu y'ubuzima mu Budage ntiyari yarakaye.
Mu Buholandi, abantu bagera kuri 3% bashobora kuba bafite udupfukamunwa, ukurikije ibipimo by'amaraso yatanzwe.
