Ingaruka z'icyorezo n'ibipimo by'urupfu bitandukanye ku bagabo n'abagore.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa no mu Butaliyani bwagaragaje ko abagabo ari bo bapfa cyane.
Itsinda ry'abafite ibyago byinshi cyane  ni abagabo bafite imyaka 50 n'iyirenga; itandukaniro hagati y'abagabo n'abagore rirushaho kugabanuka nyuma y'imyaka 90.
Mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abapfa wari 2.8 ku ijana by'abagabo n'1.7 ku ijana by'abagore.
Impamvu nyayo zituma habaho ibyo gutandukana ntiziramenyekana, ariko zishobora kuba zishingiye ku bumenyi bw'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima n'imyifatire y'abantu.
Itandukaniro ry'imiti y'igitsina gore, kugabanuka kw'abagore batanywa itabi, indwara ziterwa n'itabi mu bagabo (urugero, indwara y'umuvuduko w'amaraso mu bagabo, igaragara mu gihe bakiri bato kurusha abagore) bishobora gutuma abagabo bapfa cyane.
Mu Burayi, 57% by'abanduye bari abagabo, na 72% by'abapfuye bazira COVID-19 bari abagabo.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, leta ya Amerika nta mibare y'ibitsina ifite kuri COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko indwara ziterwa na virusi, urugero nka Ebola, SIDA, ibicurane na SARS, zifite imibare itandukanye y'ibitsina.
Abakozi benshi mu by'ubuzima, cyane cyane mu by'ubuvuzi, ni abagore, bityo bakaba bafite amahirwe menshi yo kwandura.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, Umuryango Mpuzamahanga wita ku Buzima watangaje izina ry'iki cyorezo  COVID-19.
Umuyobozi wa OMS, Bwana Tedros Adanoum Gebreissus, asobanura ko CO ari korona, VI virusi, D  indwara, kandi ko umwaka wa 19 ari wo wa mbere iki cyorezo cyagaragaye: 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Izina ry'iki cyorezo ryatoranyijwe kugira ngo hatagira umuntu ushyiraho izina ry'ahantu runaka (urugero nk'u Bushinwa), ubwoko bw'inyamaswa cyangwa itsinda ry'abantu, nk'uko bisabwa n'amazina mpuzamahanga agamije kwirinda gutesha agaciro. Virusi itera COVID-19 yitwa SARS-CoV-2.
Mu butumwa bwa WHO, ikoresha andi magambo virusi ya COVID-19 na virusi itera COVID-19.
Iyo ndwara n'iyo virusi ubwabyo, ubusanzwe byitwa "coronavirus".
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere cyabereye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, virusi n'indwara byitwaga coronavirus na Huhan coronavirus.
Muri Mutarama 2020, hakurikijwe amabwiriza yo mu 2015 ku bijyanye no gukoresha ahantu h'akarere mu mazina y'indwara na virusi, OMS yasabye ko hakoreshwa amagambo Indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze 2019-nCov na 2019-nCoV nk'amazina y'agateganyo ya virusi n'indwara.
Tariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, amazina yemewe   COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 yashyizwe ahagaragara.
Kubera ko hari ibigo by'ikoranabuhanga bitanga serivisi z'ikoranabuhanga, hari abacuruzi b'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga bicapisha ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, urugero nk'ibikoresho byo gupima mu mazuru n'ibikoresho byo mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga.
Mu gihe kimwe, ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cyo mu Butaliyani cyari gikeneye cyane valve yo guhumeka, ariko umutangabuguzi ntiyashoboye kuyitanga mu gihe cyagenwe, bityo umwe mu bakozi bo mu karere k'iwabo yahinduriwe imikorere, maze asohora valve 100 zisabwa mu ijoro rimwe.
Kuva icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangira, ibitekerezo bitandukanye by'ubugambanyi, amakuru atari yo n'amakuru y'ibinyoma ku nkomoko ya virusi, ingano yayo, kwirinda, kuvura n'ibindi, byatangiye gukwirakwira kuri interineti mu buryo bwihuse.
Birashoboka ko abantu bashobora kwanduza abandi.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi ntibyagaragaje ko virusi yandurira mu ngurube, mu duca no mu nkoko.
Kugeza ubu nta rukingo rwemewe rwo kurwanya iyi virusi cyangwa imiti yo kuyikiza.
Ubu ubushakashatsi mpuzamahanga ku nkingo na imiti ya COVID-19 burakorwa n'inzego za leta, amatsinda y'abanyeshuri n'abashakashatsi mu by'inganda.
Muri Werurwe, OMS yatangije gahunda ya SOLIDARITY Trial (Igerageza ryo GUSHIMBA) igamije gusuzuma ingaruka zo kuvura imyunyu ine iriho ubu, ibonwa ko ari yo ifite imbaraga kurusha izindi.
Kugeza ubu nta rukingo rwuzuye rubaho, ariko hari imiryango itandukanye irimo gukora cyane ku miti ishobora gukoreshwa mu gukingira abantu.
SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi byinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'umuntu hifashishijwe ACE2, bityo ubushakashatsi bukoresha ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwa mbere bwa SARS-CoV.
Hari uburyo butatu bwo gukingira.
Icya mbere, abashakashatsi bifuza gukora urukingo rw'ubwoko bwose.
Gukoresha virusi nk'iyi, yaba idafite ubuzima cyangwa se idafite ubuzima, bigamije gutuma umubiri w'umuntu ugira ubushobozi bwo kwirinda vuba bwa COVID-19.
Uburyo bwa kabiri, ni ugukora urukingo rw'ingingo ntoya, bugamije gukora urukingo rwiyongera ubushobozi bw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya ingingo ntoya z'ubwandu.
Ku kibazo cya SARS-CoV-2, ubwo bushakashatsi bugamije gusenya poroteyine ya S-chip, ifasha virusi kwinjira muri ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu  ni ugukora inkingo zishingiye ku aside ya nukleyini (inkingo za ADN cyangwa za RNA, uburyo bushya bwo gukora inkingo).
Inkingo z'igerageza zashyizweho hakurikijwe ubwo buryo, zigomba gusuzumwa ku birebana n'umutekano n'ibyazo. Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020, i Seattle hatangiye igerageza rya mbere ry'urukingo ku bantu bane bitangiye gukora.
Urukingo rugizwe na kode ya jenoside itagira icyo itwaye, ikorwa hakoreshejwe virusi ituma habaho indwara.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, hari ibyigwa by'ubuvuzi bisaga 300.
Imiti yemewe mu kuvura malariya yagenzuwe mu bigeragezo birindwi, bine muri byo byari iby'ibinyabutabire bya hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chlorohine.
Gusuzuma imiti irwanya virusi ni byo bigize igice kinini cy'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa; mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Mata, mu bihugu byinshi habaye ubushakashatsi bw'icyiciro cya III bwakozwe ku muti wa remdesivir.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, hakorewe isuzuma ryihariye ry'imiti ikoreshwa mu kuvura COVID-19 n'indi miti yifuza kuvura COVID-19. Ibi kandi bikaba ari na byo bigamije gusuzuma indi miti myinshi ikoreshwa mu kuvura COVID-19, harimo remdesivir, chlorohine na hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir, na lopinavir/ritonavir ifatanyije na interferon beta.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, hari amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko umuti wa remdesivir ukoreshwa neza.
Iterambere ry'uburwayi ryagaragaye mu barwayi bahabwa remdesivir nk'urwitwazo.
Icyiciro cya III cy'igerageza ry'ubuvuzi kirimo gukorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Gukoresha chlorokine, mbere yaho yakoreshwaga mu kuvura malariya, byasuzumwe mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, kandi hari ibisubizo bya mbere.
Icyakora, hari hakenewe ko ubushakashatsi bugenzurwa n'impuguke.
Abayobozi b'ubuzima bo muri Koreya no mu Bushinwa batanga inama yo gukoresha chlorohine.
Ikigo cya Wuhan gishinzwe kurwanya virusi gitanga igitekerezo cyo gukoresha ingano ya gram imwe ku munsi, ariko kivuga ko kongera incuro ebyiri ingano y'iyo virusi ari akaga kandi ko bishobora gutuma umuntu apfa.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha mu buryo bwihutirwa hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine mu gihe abaganga bavura abarwayi ba COVID-19 babishatse.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko dosiye nyinshi za ribavirine ari ngombwa mu kubuza SARS-CoV-2 in vitro.
Nitasoxanide yagiriwe inama yo kwigwa mu buryo burambuye in vivo, igaragaza ko ihagarika SARS-CoV-2 mu rugero rwo hasi. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko kugira ngo SARS-CoV-2 yinjire mu mubiri binyuze mu guhuza na ACE2 bisaba ko poroteyine ya poroteyine ya poroteyine ya serine 2 (TMPRSS2) ihura n'umuti.
Ubushakashatsi ku ikoreshwa rya chlorohine na hydroxychloroquine hamwe na azitromycin cyangwa ntayo bufite imipaka ikomeye ituma umuryango w'ubuvuzi udashobora gukoresha ubu buryo bwo kuvura nta kindi cyizere cy'uko bwaba bushingiye ku bushakashatsi.
Impamvu ishobora gutuma umuntu agira indwara y'uburwayi bw'uruhu (hypercytocinemia) ni uko ari ikibazo cy'indwara ya COVID-19 mu gihe cy'ibihe by'indwara zikomeye.
Hari ibimenyetso byemeza ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo gutuma umuntu agira indwara yo kugabanya ibiro byinshi. Ubushakashatsi buciriritse bwakozwe n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa, bwashyize tocilisumab mu nama z'ubuvuzi bwa coronavirus.
Uyu muti wageze mu cyiciro cya kabiri cy'igerageza ritunganijwe ku rwego rw'igihugu mu Butaliyani, nyuma yo kubona ibisubizo byiza ku barwayi bafite indwara ikomeye.
Iyo ikoreshwa ifatanyije na ferritin mu gusuzuma amaraso kugira ngo hamenyekane ibicurane bya sitokina, iba igamije kurwanya ibintu bivugwa ko bishobora gutuma abarwayi bamwe bapfa.
Mu mwaka wa 2017, FDA yemeje interleukin-6 receptor antagonist ishingiye ku bushakashatsi bw'ibanze bw'inyongera bwo kuvura syndrome yo kurekura cytocin ya steroid ikorwa n'indi mpamvu, T-cell therapy ya CAR.
Kugeza ubu, nta bimenyetso byakozwe ku buryo buteganyijwe cyangwa byateganijwe bigaragaza ko tocilisumab ari umuti w'ingirakamaro wo kuvura cytocin release syndrome.
Gutanga udupande tw'umubiri twanduye kandi tw'umubiri tw'umubiri twakozwe n'ubwirinzi bw'abarwayi bakize COVID-19 ku bantu babukeneye ubu birafatwa nk'uburyo butari ubw'inkingo bwo kuboneza urubyaro.
Ubu buryo bwashyizwe mu igerageza mu kuvura abarwayi ba SARS, ariko ibisubizo byayo ntibyashimishije.
Kugabanya virusi  ni ingaruka ziteganyijwe, aho imiti y'umubiri idakora ishobora kurinda SARS-CoV-2.
Icyakora, hari ubundi buryo bushobora gukoreshwa, urugero nk'imiti ifite ubumara bw'umubiri mu ngirabuzimafatizo cyangwa se igipimo cy'imiti ifite ubumara bw'umubiri mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Hari ubundi buryo bwo kuvura antibodies mu buryo budafite icyo bukora, urugero nko gukoresha antibodies za monoclonal zikozwe, ubu burimo gukorwa.
